{"type":"message","id":"823ff2d3","parentId":"ef08dad1","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:02:11.013Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The boss wants me to trace through the code and identify all the device read/write operations that happen concurrently when:\n1. Main console operations (normal usage - PTZ move, image parameter changes, etc.)\n2. Local focus (FocusSearcher in autofocus.py)\n3. Local white balance (WhiteBalanceSearcher in whitebalance.py)\n\nLet me now look at the key functions more closely. I need to understand:\n\n1. `startPtzImagePoll()` - the periodic polling in the main console\n2. How local focus is started (the `startAutoFocus` or similar function)\n3. How local white balance is started (the `startAutoWhiteBalance` or similar)\n4. `startLiveStack()` - continuous capture\n5. Any other concurrent operations\n\nLet me read the specific areas of interest.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Y9btMxHrUzNcfaPgOuyO1701","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":1988,"limit":120,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_c9t203KLsQBJqdjAXUiI9243","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":1300,"limit":200,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_02_K4acLyLqFkTA3wP14HU29148","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":870,"limit":120,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":51035,"output":446,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51481,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783447321981,"responseId":"cht000d2d12@dx19f3dbe849a29c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5eeb5c4b","parentId":"823ff2d3","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:02:11.024Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_Y9btMxHrUzNcfaPgOuyO1701","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"var _ptzImagePollInterval = null;\r\n\r\nfunction startPtzImagePoll() {\r\n    if (_ptzImagePollInterval) return; // 已在运行\r\n\r\n    _ptzImagePollInterval = setInterval(function() {\r\n        if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) return;\r\n\r\n        var dev = window.connectedDevice.ip;\r\n\r\n        // 1. PTZ 坐标 - v7.55: 分别更新三个元素\r\n        apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/position').then(function(r) {\r\n            if (r && r.success && r.data) {\r\n                var panEl = document.getElementById('ptzPan');\r\n                var tiltEl = document.getElementById('ptzTilt');\r\n                var zoomEl = document.getElementById('ptzZoom');\r\n                if (panEl) panEl.textContent = r.data.pan || 0;\r\n                if (tiltEl) tiltEl.textContent = r.data.tilt || 0;\r\n                if (zoomEl) zoomEl.textContent = r.data.zoom || 0;\r\n            }\r\n        }).catch(function(e) {});\r\n\r\n        // 2. 白平衡 R/B - v7.55: 只显示数值\r\n        apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance').then(function(r) {\r\n            if (r && r.success && r.data) {\r\n                var wb = r.data;\r\n                var rEl = document.getElementById('ptzWbR');\r\n                var bEl = document.getElementById('ptzWbB');\r\n                if (rEl) rEl.textContent = wb.red_gain || '--';\r\n                if (bEl) bEl.textContent = wb.blue_gain || '--';\r\n            }\r\n        }).catch(function(e) {});\r\n\r\n        // 3. 降噪空域/时域 - v7.55: 只显示数值\r\n        apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/noisereduce').then(function(r) {\r\n            if (r && r.success && r.data) {\r\n                var nr = r.data;\r\n                var sEl = document.getElementById('ptzDnrSpatial');\r\n                var tEl = document.getElementById('ptzDnrTemporal');\r\n                var spatialVal = (nr.spatial_level !== undefined && nr.spatial_level !== null) ? nr.spatial_level : '--';\r\n                var temporalVal = (nr.temporal_level !== undefined && nr.temporal_level !== null) ? nr.temporal_level : '--';\r\n                if (sEl) sEl.textContent = spatialVal;\r\n                if (tEl) tEl.textContent = temporalVal;\r\n            }\r\n        }).catch(function(e) {});\r\n\r\n        // 4. 光圈 - v8.58: 显示F-num格式 (如: F2.0表示f/2.0)\r\n        apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/iris').then(function(r) {\r\n            if (r && r.success && r.data) {\r\n                var ir = r.data;\r\n                var iEl = document.getElementById('ptzIris');\r\n                if (iEl) {\r\n                    var level = ir.current_level;\r\n                    if (level !== undefined && level !== null) {\r\n                        iEl.textContent = 'F' + (level / 100).toFixed(1);  // 如: 200 → F2.0\r\n                    } else {\r\n                        iEl.textContent = '--';\r\n                    }\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n        }).catch(function(e) {});\r\n\r\n        // 5. 快门 - v7.55: 只显示数值\r\n        apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/shutter').then(function(r) {\r\n            if (r && r.success && r.data) {\r\n                var sh = r.data;\r\n                var sEl = document.getElementById('ptzShutter');\r\n                if (sEl) sEl.textContent = sh.current_level || '--';\r\n            }\r\n        }).catch(function(e) {});\r\n    }, 1000);\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction stopPtzImagePoll() {\r\n    if (_ptzImagePollInterval) {\r\n        clearInterval(_ptzImagePollInterval);\r\n        _ptzImagePollInterval = null;\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 暴露到全局\r\nwindow.startPtzImagePoll = startPtzImagePoll;\r\nwindow.stopPtzImagePoll = stopPtzImagePoll;\r\n\r\n// ==================== 暴露到全局 ====================\r\nwindow.toggleSection = toggleSection;\r\nwindow.loadDeviceImageParams = loadDeviceImageParams;\r\nwindow.setSharpness = setSharpness;\r\nwindow.setWhiteBalanceMode = setWhiteBalanceMode;\r\nwindow.setWhiteBalanceGain = setWhiteBalanceGain;\r\nwindow.setNoiseReduce = setNoiseReduce;\r\nwindow.loadFilterStatus = loadFilterStatus;\r\nwindow.setDayNightMode = setDayNightMode;\r\nwindow.setShutterSpeed = setShutterSpeed;\r\nwindow.setIris = setIris;\r\nwindow.setExposureMode = setExposureMode;\r\nwindow.togglePtzOsd = togglePtzOsd;\r\nwindow.toggleInfoOsd = toggleInfoOsd;\r\nwindow.updatePtzOsdButtons = updatePtzOsdButtons;\r\nwindow.updateInfoOsdButtons = updateInfoOsdButtons;\r\nwindow.setSlowShutter = setSlowShutter;\r\nwindow.loadSlowShutter = loadSlowShutter;\r\n// v7.32: 新增功能检测相关函数\r\nwindow.goToFunctionTest = goToFunctionTest;\r\nwindow.showFunctionOverlay = showFunctionOverlay;\r\nwindow.removeFunctionOverlay = removeFunctionOverlay;\r\n// v8.38: 白平衡/对焦模式切换 + 停止函数\r\nwindow.onWbModeChange = onWbModeChange;\r\nwindow.onFocusModeChange = onFocusModeChange;\r\nwindow.stopAutoWhiteBalance = stopAutoWhiteBalance;\r\nwindow.stopAutoFocus = stopAutoFocus;\r\n// v8.58: consoleSnapshot函数已移至console.html单独定义\r\nwindow.consoleSnapshot = consoleSnapshot;\r\n</script>\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783447331024}}
{"type":"message","id":"1e3e5ec0","parentId":"5eeb5c4b","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:02:11.025Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_01_c9t203KLsQBJqdjAXUiI9243","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    var confirmBtn = document.getElementById('btnWbTimerConfirm');\r\n    var selectBtn = document.getElementById('btnWbRegionSelect');\r\n    if (stopBtn) stopBtn.disabled = true;\r\n    if (confirmBtn) { confirmBtn.disabled = true; confirmBtn.style.opacity = '0.5'; }\r\n    if (selectBtn) { selectBtn.style.opacity = '1'; }\r\n    selectBtn.style.opacity = '1';\r\n    stopWbTimer();\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 对焦模式切换:显示/隐藏对应控件\r\nfunction onFocusModeChange(mode) {\r\n    var moveControls = document.getElementById('focusMoveControls');\r\n    var localControls = document.getElementById('focusLocalControls');\r\n\r\n    if (mode === 'manual') {\r\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'block';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        setFocusMode('manual');\r\n        stopFocusTimer();\r\n        var toggle = document.getElementById('focusTimerToggle');\r\n        if (toggle) toggle.checked = false;\r\n    } else if (mode === 'local') {\r\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'block';\r\n    } else {\r\n        // 自动\r\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        setFocusMode('auto');\r\n        stopFocusTimer();\r\n        var toggle = document.getElementById('focusTimerToggle');\r\n        if (toggle) toggle.checked = false;\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 停止自动对焦\r\nfunction stopAutoFocus() {\r\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n    if (!dev) return;\r\n    if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('用户停止', 'warning');\r\n    apiPost('/api/v1/vision/focus-stop', {}).then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success) {\r\n            showToast('success', '已停止对焦搜索');\r\n        }\r\n    }).catch(function(e) {\r\n        showToast('error', '停止失败');\r\n    });\r\n    // 恢复按钮状态\r\n    var stopBtn = document.getElementById('btnFocusLocalStop');\r\n    var confirmBtn = document.getElementById('btnFocusTimerConfirm');\r\n    var selectBtn = document.getElementById('btnFocusRegionSelect');\r\n    if (stopBtn) stopBtn.disabled = true;\r\n    if (confirmBtn) { confirmBtn.disabled = true; confirmBtn.style.opacity = '0.5'; }\r\n    if (selectBtn) { selectBtn.style.opacity = '1'; }\r\n    selectBtn.style.opacity = '1';\r\n    stopFocusTimer();\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v8.41: 白平衡定时器\r\nfunction updateWbTimerInput(input) {\r\n    input.value = input.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '');\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction updateFocusTimerInput(input) {\r\n    input.value = input.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '');\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction toggleWbTimer() {\r\n    var toggle = document.getElementById('wbTimerToggle');\r\n    var input = document.getElementById('wbTimerInput');\r\n    if (!toggle || !input) return;\r\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\r\n    if (minutes <= 0) {\r\n        toggle.checked = false;\r\n        showToast('warning', '请输入大于0的分钟数');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    if (toggle.checked) {\r\n        var region = localStorage.getItem('region_whitebalance');\r\n        if (!region) {\r\n            toggle.checked = false;\r\n            showToast('warning', '请先框选区域');\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        stopWbTimer();\r\n        wbTimerSeconds = minutes * 60;\r\n        updateWbTimerDisplay();\r\n        wbTimerId = setInterval(function() {\r\n            wbTimerSeconds--;\r\n            updateWbTimerDisplay();\r\n            if (wbTimerSeconds <= 0) {\r\n                clearInterval(wbTimerId);\r\n                wbTimerId = null;\r\n                executeScheduledSearch('whitebalance');\r\n            }\r\n        }, 1000);\r\n        showToast('success', '白平衡定时已启动: ' + minutes + '分钟');\r\n    } else {\r\n        stopWbTimer();\r\n        showToast('info', '白平衡定时已关闭');\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction toggleFocusTimer() {\r\n    var toggle = document.getElementById('focusTimerToggle');\r\n    var input = document.getElementById('focusTimerInput');\r\n    if (!toggle || !input) return;\r\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\r\n    if (minutes <= 0) {\r\n        toggle.checked = false;\r\n        showToast('warning', '请输入大于0的分钟数');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    if (toggle.checked) {\r\n        var region = localStorage.getItem('region_focus');\r\n        if (!region) {\r\n            toggle.checked = false;\r\n            showToast('warning', '请先框选区域');\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        stopFocusTimer();\r\n        focusTimerSeconds = minutes * 60;\r\n        updateFocusTimerDisplay();\r\n        focusTimerId = setInterval(function() {\r\n            focusTimerSeconds--;\r\n            updateFocusTimerDisplay();\r\n            if (focusTimerSeconds <= 0) {\r\n                clearInterval(focusTimerId);\r\n                focusTimerId = null;\r\n                executeScheduledSearch('focus');\r\n            }\r\n        }, 1000);\r\n        showToast('success', '对焦定时已启动: ' + minutes + '分钟');\r\n    } else {\r\n        stopFocusTimer();\r\n        showToast('info', '对焦定时已关闭');\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction stopWbTimer() {\r\n    if (wbTimerId) { clearInterval(wbTimerId); wbTimerId = null; }\r\n    wbTimerSeconds = 0;\r\n    var display = document.getElementById('wbTimerDisplay');\r\n    if (display) display.textContent = '';\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction stopFocusTimer() {\r\n    if (focusTimerId) { clearInterval(focusTimerId); focusTimerId = null; }\r\n    focusTimerSeconds = 0;\r\n    var display = document.getElementById('focusTimerDisplay');\r\n    if (display) display.textContent = '';\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction updateFocusTimerDisplay() {\r\n    var display = document.getElementById('focusTimerDisplay');\r\n    if (!display) return;\r\n    if (focusTimerSeconds <= 0) { display.textContent = ''; return; }\r\n    var m = Math.floor(focusTimerSeconds / 60);\r\n    var s = focusTimerSeconds % 60;\r\n    display.textContent = '(' + m + ':' + (s < 10 ? '0' : '') + s + ')';\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v8.65: 定时触发执行（使用保存的选区）- 流程开始暂停轮询，结束恢复\r\nfunction executeScheduledSearch(mode) {\r\n    var regionStr = localStorage.getItem('region_' + mode);\r\n    if (!regionStr) {\r\n        showToast('warning', (mode === 'whitebalance' ? '白平衡' : '对焦') + '无保存选区');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice;\r\n    if (!dev || !dev.ip) { showToast('error', '未连接设备'); return; }\r\n    var region = JSON.parse(regionStr);\r\n    var endpoint = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-search' : '/api/v1/vision/focus-search';\r\n    var label = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '白平衡' : '对焦';\r\n    showToast('info', label + '定时执行中...');\r\n    operationLog('── ' + label + '定时执行 ──', 'info');\r\n\r\n    // v8.65: 流程开始，暂停主控台轮询\r\n    stopPtzImagePoll();\r\n\r\n    var body = JSON.stringify({ x: region.x, y: region.y, w: region.w, h: region.h });\r\n    fetch(endpoint, { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: body })\r\n        .then(function(resp) {\r\n            if (!resp.ok) throw new Error('HTTP ' + resp.status);\r\n            var reader = resp.body.getReader();\r\n            var decoder = new TextDecoder();\r\n            var buf = '';\r\n            function pump() {\r\n                return reader.read().then(function(r) {\r\n                    if (r.done) return;\r\n                    buf += decoder.decode(r.value, { stream: true });\r\n                    var parts = buf.split('\\n\\n');\r\n                    buf = parts.pop();\r\n                    for (var i = 0; i < parts.length; i++) {\r\n                        var line = parts[i];\r\n                        if (!line.startsWith('data: ')) continue;\r\n                        try {\r\n                            var ev = JSON.parse(line.slice(6));\r\n                            if (ev.type === 'wb' || ev.type === 'focus') {\r\n                                operationLog('调整 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.stage + ' R=' + ev.red_gain + ' B=' + ev.blue_gain + ' Δ=' + ev.delta, 'info');\r\n\n[603 more lines in file. Use offset=1500 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783447331024}}
{"type":"message","id":"3e84da82","parentId":"1e3e5ec0","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:02:11.025Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_02_K4acLyLqFkTA3wP14HU29148","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"}\r\n\r\n// v7.32: 加载所有图像参数\r\nfunction loadAllImageParams(deviceIp) {\r\n    loadExposure(deviceIp);\r\n    loadOsdStatus(deviceIp);\r\n    loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp);\r\n    loadNoiseReduce(deviceIp);\r\n    loadFilterStatus(deviceIp);\r\n    loadSlowShutter(deviceIp);\r\n    loadShutter(deviceIp);\r\n    loadIris(deviceIp);\r\n    loadSharpness(deviceIp);\r\n    loadColorParams(deviceIp);\r\n    loadGain(deviceIp);\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v7.32: 显示功能检测覆盖层\r\nfunction showFunctionOverlay() {\r\n    var section = document.getElementById('imageControlSection');\r\n    if (!section) return;\r\n\r\n    // 移除旧覆盖层\r\n    var oldOverlay = document.getElementById('function-required-overlay');\r\n    if (oldOverlay) oldOverlay.remove();\r\n\r\n    // 创建覆盖层\r\n    var overlay = document.createElement('div');\r\n    overlay.id = 'function-required-overlay';\r\n    overlay.style.cssText = 'position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;background:rgba(13,17,23,0.9);z-index:100;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;padding:20px;';\r\n    overlay.innerHTML = '<div style=\"color:#f0883e;font-size:14px;text-align:center\">请执行功能检测</div><div style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:12px;text-align:center\">以启用此功能</div><button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" onclick=\"goToFunctionTest()\" style=\"margin-top:8px\">前往功能检测</button>';\r\n\r\n    section.style.position = 'relative';\r\n    section.appendChild(overlay);\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v7.32: 移除功能检测覆盖层\r\nfunction removeFunctionOverlay() {\r\n    var overlay = document.getElementById('function-required-overlay');\r\n    if (overlay) overlay.remove();\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v7.32: 跳转到功能检测页面\r\nfunction goToFunctionTest() {\r\n    // 移除覆盖层\r\n    removeFunctionOverlay();\r\n    // 跳转到高级功能页面\r\n    document.querySelector('[data-page=\"advanced\"]').click();\r\n    // 选择功能检测\r\n    setTimeout(function() {\r\n        document.querySelector('[data-test=\"function\"]').click();\r\n    }, 500);\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 加载 OSD 状态\r\nfunction loadOsdStatus(deviceIp) {\r\n    // PTZ OSD\r\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/osd/ptz').then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success) {\r\n            var enabled = r.enabled || r.data?.enabled || false;\r\n            updatePtzOsdButtons(enabled);\r\n            // 保存到 localStorage\r\n            localStorage.setItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp, enabled ? '1' : '0');\r\n        } else {\r\n            // 从 localStorage 读取上次设置\r\n            var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp);\r\n            if (saved !== null) {\r\n                updatePtzOsdButtons(saved === '1');\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    }).catch(function(e) {\r\n        var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_ptz_' + deviceIp);\r\n        if (saved !== null) {\r\n            updatePtzOsdButtons(saved === '1');\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n\r\n    // Info OSD\r\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/osd/info').then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success) {\r\n            var enabled = r.enabled || r.data?.enabled || false;\r\n            updateInfoOsdButtons(enabled);\r\n            localStorage.setItem('osd_info_' + deviceIp, enabled ? '1' : '0');\r\n        } else {\r\n            var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_info_' + deviceIp);\r\n            if (saved !== null) {\r\n                updateInfoOsdButtons(saved === '1');\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    }).catch(function(e) {\r\n        var saved = localStorage.getItem('osd_info_' + deviceIp);\r\n        if (saved !== null) {\r\n            updateInfoOsdButtons(saved === '1');\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction updatePtzOsdButtons(enabled) {\r\n    var btnOn = document.getElementById('btnPtzOsdOn');\r\n    var btnOff = document.getElementById('btnPtzOsdOff');\r\n    if (btnOn && btnOff) {\r\n        if (enabled) {\r\n            btnOn.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-primary';\r\n            btnOff.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-secondary';\r\n        } else {\r\n            btnOn.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-secondary';\r\n            btnOff.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-primary';\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    // 同步运动控制区的 PTZ OSD 开关\r\n    var sw = document.getElementById('ptzOsdSwitch');\r\n    if (sw) sw.checked = enabled;\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction updateInfoOsdButtons(enabled) {\r\n    var btnOn = document.getElementById('btnInfoOsdOn');\r\n    var btnOff = document.getElementById('btnInfoOsdOff');\r\n    if (btnOn && btnOff) {\r\n        if (enabled) {\r\n            btnOn.className = 'btn btn-sm btn-primary';\r\n\n[1113 more lines in file. Use offset=990 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783447331025}}
