{"type":"message","id":"42fb44a1","parentId":"4b8b3c17","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:04:16.407Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我有了所有需要的信息。让我整理一下所有设备操作的并发情况。\n\n核心发现：\n\n**1. 主控台轮询 (startPtzImagePoll)**：每秒触发，5个GET请求（position, whitebalance, noisereduce, iris, shutter）\n\n**2. 局部对焦 (FocusSearcher)**：\n- 初始化：GET Shutter + PUT focusConfig + GET picture\n- 每步循环：PUT move → wait → PUT stop → wait delay → GET picture\n- 结束：GET picture（验证）\n\n**3. 局部白平衡 (WhiteBalanceSearcher)**：\n- 初始化：GET Shutter + GET whitebalance + PUT manual + GET picture\n- 每步循环：PUT gains → wait delay → GET picture\n- 结束：PUT final gains + wait + GET picture + PUT locked\n\n**关键问题**：`executeScheduledSearch` 中调用了 `stopPtzImagePoll()`，但手动框选触发的搜索（toggleRegionMode → 确认后）是否也停了轮询？让我查看一下手动触发的流程。\n\n从 console.html 1478 行附近的代码看，`enableImageControls` 中会调 `startPtzImagePoll()`，`disableImageControls` 中会调 `stopPtzImagePoll()`。\n\n但是关键问题：当用户手动触发框选局部对焦/白平衡时，有没有停掉轮询？\n\n让我搜索一下实际触发对焦搜索和白平衡搜索的JS函数。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Let me find the manual trigger flow for local focus/WB:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_5d8b41fe60b84579b1325702","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && Select-String -Path \"src\\web\\includes\\console.html\" -Pattern \"toggleRegionMode|executeSearch|confirmRegion|focus-search|whitebalance-search\" | ForEach-Object { \"$($_.LineNumber): $($_.Line.Trim())\" }","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":450,"cacheRead":44350,"cacheWrite":14421,"totalTokens":59227,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783447403383,"responseId":"msg_d4588c79-dc74-4d6a-b066-88ba212ea422"}}
