{"type":"message","id":"d5a69a5e","parentId":"51d91d1d","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:04:38.600Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我找到触发搜索的实际JS代码。看起来 `toggleRegionMode` 是在 index.html 中定义的，让我搜索一下。\n\n实际上，从代码结构来看：\n1. 用户在主控台点击\"框选\"按钮 → `toggleRegionMode('focus')` 或 `toggleRegionMode('whitebalance')`\n2. 用户框选区域 → 确认 → 调用 `/api/v1/vision/focus-search` 或 `/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-search`\n\n但我需要确认：手动触发搜索时，是否也调用了 `stopPtzImagePoll()`？\n\n让我搜索一下 `toggleRegionMode` 函数在哪里定义的，以及确认搜索触发的流程。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_b3a0c5353b474372938bc1c5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && Select-String -Path \"src\\web\\*.html\" -Pattern \"function toggleRegionMode|function confirmRegion|toggleRegionMode\" | ForEach-Object { \"$($_.LineNumber): $($_.Filename): $($_.Line.Trim())\" }","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":260,"cacheRead":58771,"cacheWrite":604,"totalTokens":59641,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783447456818,"responseId":"msg_7260795a-e45a-419d-a5ae-a6ba4b5c7e7a"}}
