{"type":"message","id":"0db4f018","parentId":"86143cef","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:04:47.827Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" ","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Let me read that function and its flow."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_XJqdcenY1FyzOzJWGJRU0920","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":2853,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":62317,"output":109,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62426,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783447479009,"responseId":"cht000dd4dc@dx19f3dc0f68e29bb503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8f1da121","parentId":"0db4f018","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:04:47.834Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_XJqdcenY1FyzOzJWGJRU0920","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    function toggleRegionMode(mode) {\r\n        // 新的按钮 ID（在白平衡/对焦局部控制中）\r\n        var btnWB = document.getElementById('btnWbRegionSelect');\r\n        var btnAF = document.getElementById('btnFocusRegionSelect');\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        if (_regionMode === mode) {\r\n            _regionMode = null;\r\n            if (btnWB) btnWB.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n            if (btnAF) btnAF.className = 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n            overlay.style.display = 'none';\r\n            box.style.display = 'none';\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) {\r\n            showToast('warning', '请先连接设备');\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        // v8.39: 移除手动模式限制 - 局部模式自动切换到手动\r\n        // 当选择局部框选时，自动切换到手动模式\r\n        if (mode === 'whitebalance') {\r\n            var wbMode = document.getElementById('wbMode');\r\n            if (wbMode && wbMode.value !== 'manual') {\r\n                // 自动切换到手动模式\r\n                setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        // v8.60: 点击框选时才切换设备模式\r\n        if (mode === 'focus') {\r\n            setFocusMode('area');\r\n        }\r\n        _regionMode = mode;\r\n        if (btnWB) btnWB.className = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        if (btnAF) btnAF.className = mode === 'focus' ? 'btn btn-primary btn-sm' : 'btn btn-secondary btn-sm';\r\n        overlay.style.display = 'block';\r\n        box.style.display = 'none';\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function _getOverlayPos(e) {\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var rect = overlay.getBoundingClientRect();\r\n        return { x: e.clientX - rect.left, y: e.clientY - rect.top };\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    // v8.11: 统一 ISAPI 截图 → 后端裁剪 → 迭代搜索 → 操作日志\r\n    function _finishRegion() {\r\n        var overlay = document.getElementById('regionOverlay');\r\n        var box = document.getElementById('regionBox');\r\n        var dev = window.connectedDevice;\r\n        if (!dev || !dev.ip) { showToast('error', '未连接设备'); _resetRegionUI(); return; }\r\n\r\n        var ow = overlay.offsetWidth, oh = overlay.offsetHeight;\r\n        var sx = parseInt(box.style.left) / ow;\r\n        var sy = parseInt(box.style.top) / oh;\r\n        var sw = parseInt(box.style.width) / ow;\r\n        var sh = parseInt(box.style.height) / oh;\r\n        if (sw < 0.01 || sh < 0.01) { showToast('warning', '框选区域太小'); _resetRegionUI(); return; }\r\n\r\n        var mode = _regionMode;\r\n        \r\n        // v8.39: 保存选区到 localStorage（白平衡和对焦分别保存）\r\n        var regionKey = 'region_' + mode;\r\n        localStorage.setItem(regionKey, JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh }));\r\n        \r\n        var endpoint = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-search'\r\n                                               : '/api/v1/vision/focus-search';\r\n        var label = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '白平衡' : '对焦';\r\n\r\n        _resetRegionUI();\r\n        showToast('info', label + '迭代中...');\r\n        operationLog('── ' + label + '迭代开始 ──', 'info');\r\n        \r\n        // v8.65: 流程开始，暂停主控台轮询\r\n        stopPtzImagePoll();\r\n\r\n        // v8.41: 搜索启动时启用停止按钮\r\n        var stopBtnId = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'btnWbLocalStop' : 'btnFocusLocalStop';\r\n        var stopBtn = document.getElementById(stopBtnId);\r\n        if (stopBtn) { stopBtn.disabled = false; stopBtn.style.opacity = '1'; }\r\n\r\n\n[156 more lines in file. Use offset=2933 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783447487834}}
{"type":"message","id":"08748e6d","parentId":"8f1da121","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:05:52.401Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The boss wants me to read the code and list out how many concurrent device read/write operations happen for different scenarios. I now have enough information to analyze this comprehensively.\n\nLet me organize what I've found:\n\n**Background process: startPtzImagePoll() - 1 second interval**\n- 5 GET requests per tick (all concurrent/parallel):\n  1. GET /ptz/{dev}/position → ISAPI: GET /ISAPI/PTZCtrl/channels/1/position (or similar)\n  2. GET /ptz/{dev}/image/whitebalance → ISAPI: GET /Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\n  3. GET /ptz/{dev}/image/noisereduce → ISAPI: GET /Image/channels/1/noiseReduce\n  4. GET /ptz/{dev}/image/iris → ISAPI: GET /Image/channels/1/Iris\n  5. GET /ptz/{dev}/image/shutter → ISAPI: GET /Image/channels/1/Shutter\n\nNote: These 5 calls are fired in the same setInterval tick, so they are essentially **concurrent** - 5 parallel GETs to the device.\n\n**Key finding in executeScheduledSearch / _finishRegion:**\n- `stopPtzImagePoll()` is called BEFORE the search starts\n- This stops the 5 GET/1s polling\n\nNow let me analyze each scenario:\n\n**Scenario 1: Just main console running (no local search)**\n- 5 reads/second (every 1s, all parallel): position, whitebalance, noisereduce, iris, shutter\n- Plus any user-triggered writes (PTZ move, image settings, etc.)\n\n**Scenario 2: Local Focus (FocusSearcher)**\n- ptzImagePoll stopped before search starts\n- Per-step loop:\n  - PUT focusConfiguration (1 write) - only once at start\n  - Loop per step:\n    1. move focus: PUT continuousMove → (1 write)\n    2. Wait duration (0.2s)\n    3. Stop: PUT stop (1 write)\n    4. Wait stable_delay (exposure*2 + 0.5s)\n    5. Screenshot: GET /ISAPI/Streaming/Channels/1/picture (1 read)\n  - Final step (stop action):\n    - 1 more screenshot (verification)\n  \n  So per step: **2 writes + 1 read = 3 device operations per step**\n  They are sequential (not concurrent) within each step.\n\n**Scenario 3: Local White Balance (WhiteBalanceSearcher)**\n- ptzImagePoll stopped before search starts\n- Per-step loop:\n  - Initial setup:\n    - 1 read (calc_stable_delay: GET Shutter)\n    - 1 read (read_wb_status: GET whiteBalance)\n    - 1 write (set_wb_mode: PUT manual)\n    - 1 read (screenshot)\n  - Loop per step:\n    1. Set gains: PUT whiteBalance (1 write)\n    2. Wait stable_delay\n    3. Screenshot: GET picture (1 read)\n  \n  So per step: **1 write + 1 read = 2 device operations per step**\n  They are sequential within each step.\n\n**Scenario 4: Live Stack**\n- Not a device search operation per se - it's repeated screenshots from the browser\n- Actually looking at the code, live stack is likely using the WASM capture or ISAPI screenshot at intervals\n- I should check what it does... but it probably just does screenshots at intervals\n\nActually, looking more carefully at the code, the key question the boss is asking is: **during a local focus/WB search, what's the device I/O load?**\n\nThe answer is clear:\n- ptzImagePoll is stopped → no more background 5 GETs\n- The search runs sequentially: move → wait → screenshot → compute → repeat\n- Only 1 request to device at a time (no concurrency during search)\n\nBut wait - there's also the WASM video stream! Let me check if that's also running concurrently.\n\nThe WASM stream is playing on the page. That's a WebSocket connection to the video stream proxy. That's separate from ISAPI HTTP requests. It's a continuous stream, not counted as individual read/write operations.\n\nAlso - the user might manually trigger things like PTZ move, image settings changes WHILE the local search is running. But the UI should prevent that... let me check.\n\nActually from the code, when search is running:\n- The stop button is enabled\n- The section-disabled class is NOT added (that's only for disconnected state)\n- So the user could theoretically still interact with other controls\n\nBut the key finding is: during local focus/WB search, ptzImagePoll is explicitly stopped, so no background polling contention.\n\nLet me also check if there's anything else running periodically, like OSD updates or anything else.\n\nActually, I think I have enough to give a comprehensive answer now. Let me also check the `_capture_func` to understand what it actually does - it likely goes through router.py.\n\nLet me look at the router.py vision endpoints for focus-search and whitebalance-search to see how they invoke the capture.\n","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Now let me check what the capture function actually does in the router, and whether the WASM stream adds device I/O:Now let me check the vision router endpoints to see how capture is done:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_122a349a8cca40bda8d84370","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":140,"offset":4106,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\api\\router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":6,"output":1268,"cacheRead":59375,"cacheWrite":1351,"totalTokens":62000,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783447487835,"responseId":"msg_95df6e5a-143c-4ec5-9d3a-01663e27f2ab"}}
{"type":"message","id":"32ebdb02","parentId":"08748e6d","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:05:52.408Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_122a349a8cca40bda8d84370","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@api_router.post(\"/vision/whitebalance-search\", summary=\"白平衡迭代搜索 (SSE)\", tags=[\"Vision\"])\r\nasync def whitebalance_search(data: dict):\r\n    \"\"\"白平衡迭代搜索 - SSE流式。路由层只验证输入和调用白平衡模块。\"\"\"\r\n    import json\r\n    from fastapi.responses import StreamingResponse\r\n    from src.controlpanel.whitebalance import WhiteBalanceSearcher\r\n\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': 'PTZ控制器未初始化'})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    connected = mgr.get_connected_device()\r\n    if not connected:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': '无活跃设备'})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    device_ip = connected[\"ip\"]\r\n    client, err = _get_client_for_device(mgr, device_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': err})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    x = float(data.get(\"x\", 0))\r\n    y = float(data.get(\"y\", 0))\r\n    w = float(data.get(\"w\", 0))\r\n    h = float(data.get(\"h\", 0))\r\n\r\n    if w <= 0 or h <= 0:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': '框选区域无效'})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    searcher = WhiteBalanceSearcher(\r\n        mgr=mgr, device_ip=device_ip, client=client,\r\n        x=x, y=y, w=w, h=h,\r\n        capture_func=_capture_and_crop,\r\n        cleanup_func=_cleanup_temp,\r\n        mac_clean=connected.get(\"mac\", \"\").replace(\":\", \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\").lower()\r\n    )\r\n    \r\n    # v8.41: 保存搜索器到全局变量\r\n    global _wb_searcher\r\n    _wb_searcher = searcher\r\n    \r\n    return StreamingResponse(\r\n        searcher.run(),\r\n        media_type=\"text/event-stream\",\r\n        headers={\"Cache-Control\": \"no-cache\", \"X-Accel-Buffering\": \"no\"}\r\n    )\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/vision/whitebalance-stop\", summary=\"停止白平衡搜索\", tags=[\"Vision\"])\r\nasync def whitebalance_stop():\r\n    \"\"\"停止当前白平衡搜索并写入最佳值到设备\"\"\"\r\n    global _wb_searcher\r\n    if not _wb_searcher:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"无活跃的白平衡搜索\"}\r\n    \r\n    _wb_searcher._interrupt()\r\n    _wb_searcher = None\r\n    \r\n    return {\"success\": True, \"message\": \"白平衡搜索已停止\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/vision/focus-search\", summary=\"反差对焦搜索\", tags=[\"Vision\"])\r\nasync def focus_search(data: dict):\r\n    \"\"\"反差对焦搜索 - SSE流式。路由层只验证输入和调用对焦模块。\"\"\"\r\n    import json\r\n    from fastapi.responses import StreamingResponse\r\n    from src.controlpanel.autofocus import FocusSearcher\r\n\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': 'PTZ控制器未初始化'})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    connected = mgr.get_connected_device()\r\n    if not connected:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': '无活跃设备'})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    device_ip = connected[\"ip\"]\r\n    client, err = _get_client_for_device(mgr, device_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': err})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    x = float(data.get(\"x\", 0))\r\n    y = float(data.get(\"y\", 0))\r\n    w = float(data.get(\"w\", 0))\r\n    h = float(data.get(\"h\", 0))\r\n\r\n    if w <= 0 or h <= 0:\r\n        return StreamingResponse(\r\n            iter([f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'error', 'message': '框选区域无效'})}\\n\\n\"]),\r\n            media_type=\"text/event-stream\"\r\n        )\r\n\r\n    searcher = FocusSearcher(\r\n        mgr=mgr, device_ip=device_ip, client=client,\r\n        x=x, y=y, w=w, h=h,\r\n        capture_func=_capture_and_crop,\r\n        cleanup_func=_cleanup_temp,\r\n        mac_clean=connected.get(\"mac\", \"\").replace(\":\", \"\").replace(\"-\", \"\").lower()\r\n    )\r\n    \r\n    # v8.41: 保存搜索器到全局变量\r\n    global _focus_searcher\r\n    _focus_searcher = searcher\r\n    \r\n    return StreamingResponse(\r\n        searcher.run(),\r\n        media_type=\"text/event-stream\",\r\n        headers={\"Cache-Control\": \"no-cache\", \"X-Accel-Buffering\": \"no\"}\r\n    )\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.post(\"/vision/focus-stop\", summary=\"停止对焦搜索\", tags=[\"Vision\"])\r\nasync def focus_stop():\r\n    \"\"\"停止当前对焦搜索\"\"\"\r\n    global _focus_searcher\r\n    if not _focus_searcher:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"无活跃的对焦搜索\"}\r\n    \r\n    _focus_searcher._interrupt()\r\n    _focus_searcher = None\r\n\n[77 more lines in file. Use offset=4246 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783447552407}}
