{"type":"message","id":"9e6b0808","parentId":"221beac5","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:14:23.132Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9e399816c8954eadb4510224","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n    // 移除画面控制区的旧提示(如果存在)\r\n    var oldWarning = document.getElementById('functionCacheWarning');\r\n    if (oldWarning) oldWarning.remove();\r\n\r\n    // v7.0: 停止 PTZ 坐标刷新\r\n    if (window.stopPtzImagePoll) window.stopPtzImagePoll();\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v6.20 + v7.0: 启用所有控制区域\r\nfunction enableImageControls() {\r\n    // v7.30: 移除模块禁用样式\r\n    var sections = ['ptzControlSection', 'trackControlSection', 'mediaControlSection', 'imageControlSection', 'logControlSection'];\r\n    sections.forEach(function(sectionId) {\r\n        var section = document.getElementById(sectionId);\r\n        if (section) {\r\n            section.classList.remove('section-disabled');\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n\r\n    // v7.11: 启用画面控制控件（不包括 OSD 开关，它们在运动控制）\r\n    var controls = [\r\n        'consoleBrightness', 'consoleContrast', 'consoleSaturation', 'consoleSharpness',\r\n        'wbMode', 'wbRed', 'wbBlue', 'dnrSpatial', 'dnrTemporal',\r\n        'exposureMode', 'shutterSpeed', 'irisLevel', 'gainLevel',\r\n    ];\r\n    controls.forEach(function(id) {\r\n        var el = document.getElementById(id);\r\n        if (el) {\r\n            el.disabled = false;\r\n            el.style.opacity = '1';\r\n            el.style.cursor = 'pointer';\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n\r\n    // v7.0: 启用 PTZ 控制按钮\r\n    var ptzSection = document.getElementById('ptzControlSection');\r\n    if (ptzSection) {\r\n        var ptzBtns = ptzSection.querySelectorAll('.btn, .ptz-btn');\r\n        ptzBtns.forEach(function(btn) {\r\n            if (btn.id !== 'ptzSpeed') {\r\n                btn.disabled = false;\r\n                btn.style.opacity = '1';\r\n                btn.style.cursor = 'pointer';\r\n            }\r\n        });\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    // v7.0: 启用媒体操作按钮\r\n    var mediaButtons = ['btnConsoleSnapshot', 'btnConsoleRecord', 'btnLiveStackStart', 'btnLiveStackStop', 'btnLiveStackSave'];\r\n\n[1383 more lines in file. Use offset=720 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783448063132}}
{"type":"message","id":"304f8dda","parentId":"9e6b0808","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:14:23.132Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_32486985d52446e48bbdfaa7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    // v7.01: 隐藏主控台提示框\r\n    var consoleWarning = document.getElementById('consoleWarning');\r\n    if (consoleWarning) {\r\n        consoleWarning.style.display = 'none';\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    // v7.0: 启动 PTZ 坐标刷新\r\n    if (window.startPtzImagePoll) window.startPtzImagePoll();\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 连接设备时加载图像参数(从function.json读取范围,从ISAPI读取当前值)\r\n// v6.20: 优先读取缓存,无缓存时禁用控件\r\n// v6.41: 修复下拉菜单加载中问题\r\n// 当 function.json 不存在时,仍然加载基础参数(使用默认范围)\r\n// v6.43: 刷新画面控制按钮\r\nfunction refreshImageControls() {\r\n    if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) {\r\n        console.warn('[IMAGE] No device connected');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    console.log('[IMAGE] Refreshing image controls...');\r\n    loadDeviceImageParams(window.connectedDevice.ip);\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v6.50: 重置画面控制到系统默认值\r\nfunction resetImageControls() {\r\n    if (!window.connectedDevice || !window.connectedDevice.ip) {\r\n        console.warn('[IMAGE] No device connected');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    // v7.117: 使用统一弹窗确认\r\n    showModal({\r\n        type: 'confirm',\r\n        title: '重置',\r\n        message: '确认重置画面控制到系统默认值?',\r\n        onConfirm: function() {\r\n            var dev = window.connectedDevice.ip;\r\n            console.log('[IMAGE] Resetting image controls to defaults...');\r\n\r\n            // 系统默认值\r\n            var defaults = {\r\n                brightness: 50,\r\n                contrast: 50,\r\n                saturation: 50,\r\n                sharpness: 50,\r\n                wbRed: 100,\r\n                wbBlue: 100,\r\n                dnrSpatial: 50,\r\n                dnrTemporal: 50,\r\n\n[1313 more lines in file. Use offset=790 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783448063132}}
{"type":"message","id":"b8ed3199","parentId":"304f8dda","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:14:53.839Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. So I can see:\n1. `disableImageControls()` calls `stopPtzImagePoll()` (line 676)\n2. `enableImageControls()` calls `startPtzImagePoll()` (line 747)\n\nThese are already in place, but they're only called on device connect/disconnect, not during function/speed/limit tests.\n\nLet me also look at how the function/limit/speed tests are triggered from the frontend - they need to call backend endpoints. I need to check if there's any existing polling control mechanism there.\n\nLet me also check where the function/limit/speed endpoints are called in the frontend, and if there's already any polling control. Let me also look at the index.html context around line 2926 where stopPtzImagePoll is called.\n\nLet me also check the `index.html` around line 2926 where `stopPtzImagePoll` is called, to understand what context triggers it.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Let me check the context around where `stopPtzImagePoll` is called in index.html and understand the existing patterns:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:34","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":2920,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":60675,"output":271,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60946,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783448063134,"responseId":"cht000d49b4@dx19f3dc9d78529bb503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6983382a","parentId":"b8ed3199","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:14:53.847Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.read:34","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n        _resetRegionUI();\r\n        showToast('info', label + '迭代中...');\r\n        operationLog('── ' + label + '迭代开始 ──', 'info');\r\n        \r\n        // v8.65: 流程开始，暂停主控台轮询\r\n        stopPtzImagePoll();\r\n\r\n        // v8.41: 搜索启动时启用停止按钮\r\n        var stopBtnId = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'btnWbLocalStop' : 'btnFocusLocalStop';\r\n        var stopBtn = document.getElementById(stopBtnId);\r\n        if (stopBtn) { stopBtn.disabled = false; stopBtn.style.opacity = '1'; }\r\n\r\n        // SSE 流式调用\r\n        var body = JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh });\r\n        fetch(endpoint, { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: body })\r\n            .then(function(resp) {\r\n                if (!resp.ok) throw new Error('HTTP ' + resp.status);\r\n                var reader = resp.body.getReader();\r\n                var decoder = new TextDecoder();\r\n                var buf = '';\r\n                function pump() {\r\n                    return reader.read().then(function(r) {\r\n                        if (r.done) return;\r\n                        buf += decoder.decode(r.value, { stream: true });\r\n                        // 按 \\n\\n 分割事件\r\n                        var parts = buf.split('\\n\\n');\r\n                        buf = parts.pop();  // 最后一段可能不完整\r\n                        for (var i = 0; i < parts.length; i++) {\r\n                            var line = parts[i];\r\n                            if (!line.startsWith('data: ')) continue;\r\n                            try {\r\n                                var ev = JSON.parse(line.slice(6));\r\n                                if (ev.type === 'start') {\r\n                                    operationLog(label + '开始, ' + ev.crop, 'info');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'wb') {\r\n                                    operationLog('调整 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.stage\r\n                                        + ' R=' + ev.red_gain + ' B=' + ev.blue_gain\r\n                                        + ' → R=' + ev.r_avg + ' G=' + ev.g_avg + ' B=' + ev.b_avg\r\n                                        + ' (Δ=' + ev.delta + ')', 'debug');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'focus') {\r\n                                    operationLog('对焦 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.stage\r\n                                        + ' ' + ev.action + ' 反差=' + ev.contrast\r\n                                        + ' (' + ev.duration + 's) ' + ev.message, 'debug');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'done') {\r\n                                    if (ev.final_red !== undefined) {\r\n                                        showToast('success', label + '完成 R=' + ev.final_red + ' B=' + ev.final_blue);\r\n                                        operationLog('── ' + label + '完成: R=' + ev.final_red + ' B=' + ev.final_blue + ' (' + ev.total_steps + '步) ──', 'success');\r\n                                        // 刷新主控台白平衡滑动条\r\n                                        var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\r\n                                        var wbBlue = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\r\n                                        var wbRedVal = document.getElementById('wbRedVal');\r\n                                        var wbBlueVal = document.getElementById('wbBlueVal');\r\n                                        if (wbRed) { wbRed.value = ev.final_red; if (wbRedVal) wbRedVal.textContent = ev.final_red; }\r\n                                        if (wbBlue) { wbBlue.value = ev.final_blue; if (wbBlueVal) wbBlueVal.textContent = ev.final_blue; }\r\n                                    } else {\r\n                                        var rollMsg = ev.rollback_steps ? ' (回滚' + ev.rollback_steps + '步)' : '';\r\n                                        showToast('success', label + '完成 反差=' + ev.final_contrast + rollMsg);\r\n                                        operationLog('── ' + label + '完成: 反差=' + ev.final_contrast + rollMsg + ' (' + ev.total_steps + '步) ──', 'success');\r\n                                    }\r\n\n[109 more lines in file. Use offset=2980 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783448093847}}
