{"type":"message","id":"b086a83e","parentId":"f7e08fc4","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:16:43.377Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_NJG9D2zD6B7AfLboH4dK7316","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function pollAdvProgress(taskId) {\r\n    advTaskId = taskId;\r\n    var progressEl = document.getElementById('advProgress');\r\n    var pollUrl = '/api/v1/advanced/detect/status/' + taskId;\r\n\r\n    // 清除之前的轮询\r\n    if (advPollInterval) clearInterval(advPollInterval);\r\n\r\n    // v7.53: 添加去重逻辑,避免重复输出\r\n    var lastStep = '';\r\n\r\n    advPollInterval = setInterval(function() {\r\n        fetch(pollUrl)\r\n        .then(r => r.json())\r\n        .then(data => {\r\n            if (data.success) {\r\n                // v7.52: 后端返回的字段直接在根级别(没有task包裹)\r\n                var progress = data.progress || 0;\r\n                var step = data.current_step || 'running';\r\n                var status = data.status || 'running';\r\n\r\n                // v7.52: 更新进度显示(N/M格式)\r\n                var completedItems = data.completed_items || 0;\r\n                var totalItems = data.total_items || 0;\r\n                if (progressEl) {\r\n                    if (totalItems > 0) {\r\n                        progressEl.textContent = currentAdvTest + ' (' + completedItems + '/' + totalItems + ')';\r\n                    } else {\r\n                        progressEl.textContent = currentAdvTest + ' ' + progress.toFixed(0) + '%';\r\n                    }\r\n                }\r\n\r\n                // v7.53: 实时输出当前检测端点(去重:只在步骤变化时输出)\r\n                if (step && step !== 'running' && step !== 'completed' && step !== lastStep) {\r\n                    var lastResult = data.last_result || '';\r\n                    addAdvOutput(lastResult === 'pass' ? 'success' : (lastResult === 'failed' ? 'error' : 'info'),\r\n                        '检测端点: ' + step + '...' + (lastResult || ''));\r\n                    lastStep = step;\r\n                }\r\n\r\n                // v7.53: 检查是否完成(使用getElementById获取按钮,因为是局部变量)\r\n                if (status === 'completed') {\r\n                    clearInterval(advPollInterval);\r\n                    advTaskId = null;\r\n                    addAdvOutput('success', '测试完成');\r\n                    document.getElementById('btnAdvRun').disabled = false;\r\n                    document.getElementById('btnAdvStop').disabled = true;\r\n                    // v7.54: 恢复其他页面标签\r\n                    document.querySelectorAll('.nav-btn[data-page]').forEach(function(btn) {\r\n                        btn.disabled = false;\r\n                        btn.style.opacity = '';\r\n                        btn.style.cursor = '';\r\n                    });\r\n                    // 获取最终结果\r\n                    fetchResult(taskId);\r\n                } else if (status === 'failed') {\r\n                    clearInterval(advPollInterval);\r\n                    advTaskId = null;\r\n                    addAdvOutput('error', '测试失败: ' + step);\r\n                    document.getElementById('btnAdvRun').disabled = false;\r\n                    document.getElementById('btnAdvStop').disabled = true;\r\n                    // v7.54: 恢复其他页面标签\r\n                    document.querySelectorAll('.nav-btn[data-page]').forEach(function(btn) {\r\n                        btn.disabled = false;\r\n                        btn.style.opacity = '';\r\n                        btn.style.cursor = '';\r\n                    });\r\n                    if (progressEl) progressEl.textContent = currentAdvTest + ' 失败';\r\n                } else if (status === 'cancelled') {\r\n                    clearInterval(advPollInterval);\r\n                    advTaskId = null;\r\n                    addAdvOutput('warn', '测试已取消');\r\n                    document.getElementById('btnAdvRun').disabled = false;\r\n                    document.getElementById('btnAdvStop').disabled = true;\r\n                    document.querySelectorAll('.nav-btn[data-page]').forEach(function(btn) {\r\n                        btn.disabled = false;\r\n                        btn.style.opacity = '';\r\n                        btn.style.cursor = '';\r\n                    });\r\n                    if (progressEl) progressEl.textContent = '';\r\n\n[38 more lines in file. Use offset=842 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783448203377}}
{"type":"message","id":"8bf6dfde","parentId":"b086a83e","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:17:17.618Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"  ￼Now I have all the information I need. Let me compile my analysis for the boss.\n\nLet me now check the key question from the boss:\n1. **Existing mechanisms**: What already exists?\n2. **Current behavior**: When do stop/start happen now?\n3. **Gaps**: What needs to be added?\n\nLet me also check what happens when the user navigates away from the advanced.html page while a test is running - does it stop polling?\n\nAlso I need to understand: does the WASM video player already create separate load on the device? The WASM connects to the RTSP stream, which is a separate protocol from ISAPI HTTP.\n\nLet me organize my findings:\n\n**Existing mechanism:**\n- `stopPtzImagePoll()` / `startPtzImagePoll()` already exist in console.html\n- They are called when:\n  - Device disconnect: `disableImageControls()` → `stopPtzImagePoll()`\n  - Device connect: `enableImageControls()` → `startPtzImagePoll()`\n  - Local focus/WB start: `_finishRegion()` → `stopPtzImagePoll()` (line 2926)\n  - Local focus/WB end: after `done`/`error`/`interrupt` events → `startPtzImagePoll()` (lines 2994, 3011, 3027)\n  - Local focus/WB cleanup: after `cleanup` event → `startPtzImagePoll()` (line 2986)\n\n**Current gaps:**\n1. **function/limit/speed tests**: NO call to stopPtzImagePoll/startPtzImagePoll anywhere\n2. **Timing for focus/WB**: StopPtzImagePoll is called at `_finishRegion` (before SSE fetch starts), but the first screenshot capture happens in the backend. The boss wants \"流程开始获取第一帧之前直到获取最后一帧\" - currently it starts at the right point (before the search starts) and restores after done/error/interrupt/cleanup. But there are 4 separate restore points - could be fragile.\n\n**What the boss wants:**\n1. For function/limit/speed: stop polling when test starts, restore when test finishes/fails/cancels\n2. For focus/whitebalance: guarantee stop before first frame capture, restore after last frame\n3. A unified pattern - check if there's anything to merge/inherit\n\nLet me now check: for function/limit/speed, where exactly should the stop/start be placed?\n\nCurrent flow for advanced tests:\n1. User clicks \"Run\" → `runAdvTest()` → POST `/api/v1/advanced/detect/start` → `pollAdvProgress(taskId)` starts polling\n2. `pollAdvProgress` polls `/api/v1/advanced/detect/status/{taskId}` every ~1s\n3. On completion/failure/cancellation → clearInterval + UI restore\n\nThe stopPtzImagePoll should be called before the POST to `/api/v1/advanced/detect/start`, and startPtzImagePoll should be called on completion/failure/cancellation.\n\nFor `pollAdvProgress()`, the restore happens at 3 places:\n- status === 'completed' \n- status === 'failed'\n- status === 'cancelled'\n\nAlso there's `stopAdvTest()` which handles user-initiated cancellation.\n\nSo I need to add:\n1. `stopPtzImagePoll()` before the fetch() call in the function that starts the test\n2. `startPtzImagePoll()` in all completion/cancellation paths\n\nWait, but there's also the `btnAdvStop` visible during the test. Let me check what it does.\n\nLooking at `stopAdvTest()`: it clears the polling interval, sends cancel request, and restores UI. I need to add startPtzImagePoll there too.\n\nLet me also check: when a user navigates away from the advanced page while a test is running... does the polling stop? It should since it's page-specific JS. But the backend task continues? Let me check.\n\nActually, `stopAdvTest()` doesn't call `startPtzImagePoll`. It just clears the interval. The startPoll would happen when the user returns to the console page... no wait, that's not right.\n\nLet me think about this more carefully. The polling `advPollInterval` is for the advanced test status, not for ptzImagePoll. `ptzImagePoll` is a separate interval that's always running (unless explicitly stopped).\n\nSo what I need to ensure:\n- When function/limit/speed test starts → stopPtzImagePoll\n- When function/limit/speed test ends (completes, fails, cancels) → startPtzImagePoll\n\nThis needs to happen regardless of which page the user is on. The user starts the test in advanced.html, might switch to console page while test runs.\n\nHmm, this is important. If the user switches pages:\n- The polling for status continues (setInterval is global)\n- But the startPtzImagePoll should still happen on completion\n\nWait, let me check again. `startPtzImagePoll` is defined in console.html. If the user is on advanced.html, can they still call it? Yes, because console.html is always included (it's loaded as part of index.html structure). Let me verify...\n\nActually, looking at the HTML structure: index.html includes console.html as `{% include 'includes/console.html' %}`. So console.html's JS is always loaded regardless of which \"page\" is active. Same for advanced.html which is included as `{% include 'includes/advanced.html' %}`.\n\nSo `stopPtzImagePoll` and `startPtzImagePoll` are always available globally.\n\nNow let me figure out the exact plan:\n\n**For focus/whitebalance (already partly done):**\n- Current: stop at _finishRegion(), start at cleanup/done/error/interrupt events\n- Boss wants: \"流程开始获取第一帧之前直到获取最后一帧\"\n- Analysis: The SSE flow is: stop → POST search → SSE stream starts → backend captures first frame... \n- Currently `stopPtzImagePoll()` is called BEFORE the fetch. The first capture happens in the backend (SearchSearcher.run). So stop happens before first frame. ✓\n- Restore happens after cleanup/done/error/interrupt. Last frame is captured before these events. ✓\n- **The current timing is correct.** But there are 4 restore points - could consolidate.\n\n**For function/limit/speed (not done):**\n- Need to add stopPtzImagePoll before POST /advanced/detect/start\n- Need to add startPtzImagePoll on all completion paths:\n  - status 'completed' in pollAdvProgress\n  - status 'failed' in pollAdvProgress\n  - status 'cancelled' in pollAdvProgress\n  - User stops via stopAdvTest()\n\n**Unified approach:**\n- Create wrapper functions (or just use existing stopPtzImagePoll/startPtzImagePoll directly)\n- Can the user create a \"global lock\" mechanism? Like a `_pollingPaused` counter that tracks how many concurrent operations need polling paused? This would be clean if multiple pausers exist... but in practice only one operation runs at a time.\n\nActually, thinking about it more, the simplest approach is:\n1. Create a `_pollingPauseCount` counter\n2. `pausePolling()` → increment counter, if == 1, stop ptzImagePoll\n3. `resumePolling()` → decrement counter, if == 0, start ptzImagePoll\n4. Each operation calls pause at start, resume at end\n\nThis way multiple operations can safely call pause/resume without incorrectly restarting polling.\n\nLet me now check the exact lines I need to modify and write up the report for the boss.\n\nWait, let me also check: does the `stopAdvTest()` function have a path where ptzImagePoll isn't restored? Looking at the code:\n\n```javascript\nfunction stopAdvTest() {\n    if (advPollInterval) { clearInterval(advPollInterval); advPollInterval = null; }\n    if (advTaskId) {\n        fetch('/api/v1/advanced/detect/cancel/' + advTaskId, { method: 'POST' })\n        ...\n    }\n    ...\n}\n```\n\nIt clears the interval but the backend task might still be running (the cancel is fire-and-forget). If the task eventually completes, `pollAdvProgress` won't fire the completion handler because the interval is cleared. So `startPtzImagePoll` needs to be called in `stopAdvTest` too.\n\nOK let me be comprehensive and write the report for the boss. Let me list out:\n1. What already exists\n2. What's missing\n3. Proposed approach with details\n\nLet me also check if there's a ptzPositionPoll (different from ptzImagePoll) in index.html that I haven't accounted for.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Now let me also check what `startPtzPositionPoll` is in index.html — it's separate from `startPtzImagePoll`:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Rrn3paJ9GCMbB5sGP4LX7265","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":2374,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":77233,"output":2026,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79259,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783448203378,"responseId":"cht000d6508@dx19f3dcbfa1a29bb503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"85ade696","parentId":"8bf6dfde","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:17:17.629Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_Rrn3paJ9GCMbB5sGP4LX7265","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    // PTZ position polling functions\r\n\r\n// v7.96: changeStreamType 只更新码流类型,不自动播放\r\n    // PTZ position polling\r\n\r\n// PTZ 位置自动刷新\r\nvar _ptzPosTimer = null;\r\nfunction startPtzPositionPoll() {\r\n    if (_ptzPosTimer) return;\r\n    _ptzPosTimer = setInterval(function() {\r\n        if (window.connectedDevice && window.connectedDevice.ip) {\r\n            getPtzPosition();\r\n        }\r\n    }, 1000);\r\n}\r\nfunction stopPtzPositionPoll() {\r\n    if (_ptzPosTimer) {\r\n        clearInterval(_ptzPosTimer);\r\n        _ptzPosTimer = null;\r\n    }\r\n}\r\nwindow.startPtzPositionPoll = startPtzPositionPoll;\r\nwindow.stopPtzPositionPoll = stopPtzPositionPoll;\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n    <!-- Global Functions (v5.22) -->\r\n    <script>\r\n    // 设备状态指示器更新函数\r\n\n[685 more lines in file. Use offset=2404 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783448237628}}
{"type":"message","id":"3911eaf3","parentId":"85ade696","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:18:22.053Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me compile everything I know into a comprehensive report for the boss.\n\nKey findings:\n1. There are TWO polling mechanisms:\n   - `startPtzImagePoll()` / `stopPtzImagePoll()` in console.html - 5 GETs every 1s for image parameters\n   - `startPtzPositionPoll()` / `stopPtzPositionPoll()` in index.html - 1 GET every 1s for PTZ position\n\n2. Current state:\n   - **ptpImagePoll** (console.html):\n     - Called when: device disconnect (disableImageControls), local focus/WB start/end\n     - Not called when: function/limit/speed tests run\n   - **ptpPositionPoll** (index.html):\n     - Called when: device disconnect in index.html (line 1498)\n     - Not called when: function/limit/speed tests run\n\n3. For local focus/WB:\n   - Already working: stopPtzImagePoll at _finishRegion, startPtzImagePoll at done/error/interrupt/cleanup\n   - But startPtzPositionPoll might not be stopped\n\nWait, I need to be careful here. `startPtzPositionPoll` is used for the device status indicator in the top bar (showing P/T/Z position). This is a separate thing.\n\nLet me look at where `startPtzPositionPoll` and `stopPtzPositionPoll` are called:\n\nIn index.html line 1497-1498:\n```javascript\n// Stop PTZ position polling\nif (window.stopPtzPositionPoll) window.stopPtzPositionPoll();\n```\n\nAnd... I need to find where it's started.\n\nLet me search for where stopPtzPositionPoll and startPtzPositionPoll are called in index.html.\n\nActually, looking at the code:\n- `startPtzPositionPoll` is called... probably when a device connects\n- `stopPtzPositionPoll` is called... probably when a device disconnects\n\nBut the key question is: does the advanced test (function/limit/speed) need to also pause this? The boss asked about \"主控台轮询\" which I believe refers to `startPtzImagePoll` (the image parameter polling), not `startPtzPositionPoll`.\n\nThe boss said \"主控台的轮询\" which is the 5 GETs in `startPtzImagePoll`. The position poll (`startPtzPositionPoll`) is for the top bar status indicator.\n\nBut the boss might also mean both. Let me clarify in the report.\n\nNow let me write the report. I need to:\n\n1. Summarize what exists:\n   - stopPtzImagePoll / startPtzImagePoll already implemented\n   - stopPtzPositionPoll / startPtzPositionPoll already implemented (separate mechanism)\n   \n2. Summarize current behavior:\n   - For focus/WB: stopPtzImagePoll called at search start, startPtzImagePoll at done/error/interrupt/cleanup ✓\n   - For function/limit/speed: NO calls to stop/start polling ✗\n\n3. Propose a unified approach:\n   - Option A: Simple approach - add stopPtzImagePoll/startPtzImagePoll directly\n   - Option B: Unified wrapper with counter (for robustness)\n\nLet me be concise and direct as the boss wants.\n\nActually, I also need to check one more thing: does the `pollAdvProgress` function have a `stopPtzImagePoll`/`startPtzImagePoll` anywhere? Let me verify by reading the relevant lines.\n\nActually, I already searched and found no instances of these calls in advanced.html. So the answer is: NO, the advanced tests don't currently stop the polling.\n\nAlso, I should check: for the function/limit/speed tests, do they run on the same thread as the polling? No, the polling is a frontend setInterval, the tests are backend tasks. The frontend polls for status every 1s while the test runs. So the polling and the test run concurrently.\n\nNow let me finalize my report.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a comprehensive understanding. Let me compile the report for the boss."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.write:43","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 主控台轮询暂停机制 - 分析报告\n\n**时间**: 2026-07-08\n**任务**: 为主控台轮询添加暂停/恢复机制\n\n---\n\n## 一、现有机制盘点\n\n### 1. 存在两个轮询系统\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  system1: ptzImagePoll (console.html, 1990行)       │\n│    - 频率: 1次/秒                                     │\n│    - 内容: 5个并行GET                                 │\n│      • position    → /PTZCtrl/channels/1/position   │\n│      • whitebalance → /Image/channels/1/whiteBalance │\n│      • noisereduce  → /Image/channels/1/noiseReduce  │\n│      • iris        → /Image/channels/1/iris          │\n│      • shutter     → /Image/channels/1/shutter       │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  system2: ptzPositionPoll (index.html, 2381行)      │\n│    - 频率: 1次/秒                                     │\n│    - 内容: 1个GET                                     │\n│      • position → /PTZCtrl/channels/1/position       │\n│    - 用途: 顶部状态栏显示P/T/Z坐标                    │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### 2. 现有调用链\n\n**主控台轮询 (ptzImagePoll)**\n\n| 触发点 | 文件 | 行号 | 动作 |\n|--------|------|------|------|\n| 设备断开 | console.html | 676 | `stopPtzImagePoll()` |\n| 设备连接 | console.html | 747 | `startPtzImagePoll()` |\n| 框选搜索开始 | index.html | 2926 | `stopPtzImagePoll()` |\n| done事件 | index.html | 2986 | `startPtzImagePoll()` |\n| error事件 | index.html | 3011 | `startPtzImagePoll()` |\n| interrupt事件 | index.html | 3027 | `startPtzImagePoll()` |\n\n**位置轮询 (ptzPositionPoll)**\n\n| 触发点 | 文件 | 行号 | 动作 |\n|--------|------|------|------|\n| 设备断开 | index.html | 1498 | `stopPtzPositionPoll()` |\n| 设备连接 | *(未完整搜索)* | - | `startPtzPositionPoll()` |\n\n---\n\n## 二、问题定位\n\n### ❌ 缺失：function/limit/speed 测试暂停轮询\n\n当前 `advanced.html` 的测试流程：\n\n```\n用户点击\"Run\"\n  ↓\nPOST /api/v1/advanced/detect/start\n  ↓\n轮询 /api/v1/advanced/detect/status/{taskId}\n  ↓\n[测试期间: backend 大量 ISAPI 操作]\n  ↓\ncompleted/failed/cancelled\n```\n\n**问题**: 测试全程没有调用 `stopPtzImagePoll()`，主控台5次GET/秒持续运行，与测试并发抢占设备。\n\n### ✅ 已有：局部对焦/白平衡暂停轮询\n\n当前 `index.html` 的框选搜索流程：\n\n```\n_finishRegion()\n  ↓\nstopPtzImagePoll()       ← 搜索开始前暂停 ✓\n  ↓\nfetch POST /vision/focus-search (SSE)\n  ↓\n... 搜索进行中 ...\n  ↓\nevent === 'cleanup' → startPtzImagePoll()  ← 搜索结束后恢复 ✓\nevent === 'done'    → startPtzImagePoll()  ← 恢复 ✓\nevent === 'error'   → startPtzImagePoll()  ← 恢复 ✓\nevent === 'interrupt'→ startPtzImagePoll()  ← 恢复 ✓\n```\n\n**结论**: 局部搜索的暂停/恢复已经正确实现。但恢复点分散在4个事件分支中。\n\n---\n\n## 三、建议方案\n\n### 方案A: 直接添加（最小改动）\n\n在 `advanced.html` 的 `runAdvTest()` 和 `pollAdvProgress()` 中添加 `stopPtzImagePoll`/`startPtzImagePoll`:\n\n```javascript\n// runAdvTest() 中, fetch之前添加:\nstopPtzImagePoll();\n\n// pollAdvProgress() 中, 3个完成状态分支各添加:\nstartPtzImagePoll();\n\n// stopAdvTest() 中添加:\nstartPtzImagePoll();\n```\n\n**优点**: 改动最小, 直接复用现有函数\n**缺点**: 恢复点分散, 如果有更多场景需要类似处理会重复代码\n\n### 方案B: 统一封装器（推荐）\n\n创建计数器保护机制:\n\n```javascript\n// 统一轮询暂停器\nvar _pollPauseCount = 0;\n\nfunction pausePtzPolling() {\n    _pollPauseCount++;\n    if (_pollPauseCount === 1) {\n        stopPtzImagePoll();\n        // stopPtzPositionPoll(); // 如需同时暂停\n    }\n}\n\nfunction resumePtzPolling() {\n    if (_pollPauseCount <= 0) return;\n    _pollPauseCount--;\n    if (_pollPauseCount === 0) {\n        startPtzImagePoll();\n        // startPtzPositionPoll(); // 如需同时恢复\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**优点**: \n- 计数器保护, 多个并发暂停需求可叠加\n- 集中管理, 恢复点统一\n- 未来新增暂停场景只需加一对 pause/resume\n\n**缺点**: 改动量比方案A稍大\n\n---\n\n## 四、具体改动点清单\n\n### 如果采用方案A（直接添加）\n\n**文件**: `src/web/includes/advanced.html`\n\n| 函数 | 行号 | 添加代码 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| `runAdvTest()` | fetch前 | `stopPtzImagePoll();` |\n| `pollAdvProgress()` | completed分支 | `startPtzImagePoll();` |\n| `pollAdvProgress()` | failed分支 | `startPtzImagePoll();` |\n| `pollAdvProgress()` | cancelled分支 | `startPtzImagePoll();` |\n| `stopAdvTest()` | 末尾 | `startPtzImagePoll();` |\n\n### 如果采用方案B（统一封装器）\n\n**新增位置**: `index.html` 或 `console.html`（全局可用）\n\n```javascript\n// 在 startPtzImagePoll/stopPtzImagePoll 定义后添加\nvar _pollPauseCount = 0;\nfunction pausePtzPolling() {\n    _pollPauseCount++;\n    if (_pollPauseCount === 1) stopPtzImagePoll();\n}\nfunction resumePtzPolling() {\n    if (_pollPauseCount <= 0) return;\n    _pollPauseCount--;\n    if (_pollPauseCount === 0) startPtzImagePoll();\n}\n```\n\n**替换位置**:\n\n| 文件 | 函数 | 原代码 | 替换为 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|\n| index.html | `_finishRegion()` | `stopPtzImagePoll()` | `pausePtzPolling()` |\n| index.html | 4个event分支 | `startPtzImagePoll()` | `resumePtzPolling()` |\n| advanced.html | `runAdvTest()` | *(无)* | `pausePtzPolling()` |\n| advanced.html | 4个完成分支 | *(无)* | `resumePtzPolling()` |\n\n---\n\n## 五、关于局部对焦/白平衡的补充说明\n\n现有代码已正确实现:\n- 暂停时机: `_finishRegion()` 中, 发送SSE请求前 → 早于\"获取第一帧\" ✓\n- 恢复时机: 收到 `cleanup`/`done`/`error`/`interrupt` 事件后 → 晚于\"获取最后一帧\" ✓\n\n但恢复逻辑分散在4个分支, 可优化为统一 `finally`-style:\n\n```javascript\n// 建议在 fetch().then().catch() 的 .finally() 中统一恢复\n// 或使用 try/finally 包装\n```\n\n---\n\n## 六、待审批问题\n\n1. **是否采用方案B（统一封装器）？**\n2. **是否同时暂停 ptzPositionPoll（顶部状态栏轮询）？**\n3. **局部搜索的恢复逻辑是否需要统一集中到 finally？**\n\n请审批后执行。\n","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\reports\\ptp-poll-analysis.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":69005,"output":2926,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71931,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783448237630,"responseId":"cht000de686@dx19f3dcc9cd729c2503"}}
