{"type":"message","id":"8e99c620","parentId":"b98749ba","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:37:17.022Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to modify the `_finishRegion()` function in index.html. Currently the 4 recovery branches are scattered in the event handling. Let me see the current code and refactor it.\n\nThe current structure is:\n```javascript\n// Inside _finishRegion() after SSE fetch:\nfetch(endpoint, { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: body })\n    .then(function(resp) {\n        if (!resp.ok) throw new Error('HTTP ' + resp.status);\n        var reader = resp.body.getReader();\n        var decoder = new TextDecoder();\n        var buf = '';\n        function pump() {\n            return reader.read().then(function(r) {\n                if (r.done) return;\n                buf += decoder.decode(r.value, { stream: true });\n                var parts = buf.split('\\n\\n');\n                buf = parts.pop();\n                for (var i = 0; i < parts.length; i++) {\n                    var line = parts[i];\n                    if (!line.startsWith('data: ')) continue;\n                    try {\n                        var ev = JSON.parse(line.slice(6));\n                        if (ev.type === 'wb') {\n                            // ... wb handling\n                        } else if (ev.type === 'focus') {\n                            // ... focus handling\n                        } else if (ev.type === 'done') {\n                            // handle done + startPtzImagePoll()\n                            if (ev.final_red !== undefined) {\n                                // ... wb done\n                            } else {\n                                // ... focus done\n                            }\n                            // startPtzImagePoll()\n                        } else if (ev.type === 'cleanup') {\n                            // handle cleanup + startPtzImagePoll()\n                        } else if (ev.type === 'error') {\n                            // handle error + startPtzImagePoll()\n                        } else if (ev.type === 'interrupt') {\n                            // handle interrupt + startPtzImagePoll()\n                        }\n                    } catch(e) { /* 跳过损坏的 JSON */ }\n                }\n                return pump();\n            });\n        }\n        return pump();\n    })\n    .catch(function(e) {\n        // handle error + startPtzImagePoll()\n    });\n```\n\nThe problem is: `startPtzImagePoll()` is called in 4 different places (done, cleanup, error, interrupt) plus 1 in catch.\n\nI need to refactor this to use a `finally`-like pattern. Since we're using promise chains, I can use `.finally()`.\n\nActually, since the `pump()` function is recursive, the `finally` would need to be on the outer promise. Let me think...\n\nActually, the simplest approach is:\n1. Remove all 4 `startPtzImagePoll()` calls from inside event handlers\n2. Add a flag like `_searchActive` that tracks whether the search is running\n3. Call `startPtzImagePoll()` only in `.catch()` and after the final `return pump()`\n\nWait, but `pump()` returns a promise that resolves when the reader is done. So we can chain `.then()` or `.finally()` after the outer `return pump()`.\n\nActually, looking more carefully:\n\n```javascript\nreturn reader.read().then(function(r) {\n    if (r.done) return;  // reader finished, but this returns undefined\n    // ... process events\n    return pump();  // recursive call\n});\n```\n\nThe recursive `return pump()` means the inner promise resolves when the stream ends. But the outer `return pump()` is not directly chained.\n\nLet me trace it:\n1. `_finishRegion()` calls `fetch(endpoint).then(resp => { ... return pump(); }).catch(e => { ... })`\n2. `pump()` returns `reader.read().then(...)` \n3. Inside the inner `then`, if `r.done`, it returns (undefined)\n4. If not done, it calls `return pump()` (recursive)\n5. So the inner `then` returns the recursive pump promise\n\nSo the chain is: `fetch().then(resp => pump()).catch(e => ...)`\n\nThe `.catch()` catches any error in the chain. But the \"done\" event and \"cleanup\" event are just data events, not errors.\n\nTo add a `finally`-like behavior, I need to know when the stream is truly finished. Let me think...\n\nActually, the stream ends when `reader.read()` returns `r.done === true`. At that point, the recursive `return pump()` resolves with `undefined`. So the outer `.then()` resolves.\n\nBut in the current code, `startPtzImagePoll()` is called inside event handlers when `ev.type === 'done'` or `'cleanup'` or `'error'`. The `'error'` event comes from the server, not an actual JS error. And `'cleanup'` might come after `'done'`.\n\nHmm, this is getting complex. Let me look at the actual backend to understand the event sequence.\n\nLooking at the autofocus.py:\n1. `yield` start event\n2. For each step: yield focus event\n3. When done: yield done event\n4. Then: cleanup\n5. Then: yield cleanup event\n\nSo the sequence is: start → (focus × N) → done → cleanup\n\nFor whitebalance:\n1. yield start event\n2. For each step: yield wb event\n3. When done: yield done event\n4. cleanup\n5. yield cleanup event\n\nSo `cleanup` always comes after `done`. The `startPtzImagePoll()` is called in both `done` and `cleanup` handlers. Currently this means:\n- When `done` is received: startPtzImagePoll() called\n- When `cleanup` is received: startPtzImagePoll() called again (idempotent, no harm)\n\nFor error events:\n- When `error` is received: startPtzImagePoll() called\n- When `interrupt` is received: startPtzImagePoll() called\n\nAnd in the `.catch()`: startPtzImagePoll() called for fetch-level errors.\n\nThe issue: `startPtzImagePoll()` is called multiple times for the same stream. This is idempotent (checks if already running), so it works. But it's redundant.\n\n**My approach**: Move `startPtzImagePoll()` out of event handlers and into a single place that runs after the stream is fully consumed or errors out.\n\nSince `pump()` is recursive, I can add a flag to track when the stream is done:\n\n```javascript\nvar _streamFinished = false;\n\nfunction pump() {\n    return reader.read().then(function(r) {\n        if (r.done) {\n            _streamFinished = true;\n            return;  // Stream finished normally\n        }\n        // ... process events ...\n        return pump();\n    });\n}\n\n// After pump resolves:\npump().then(function() {\n    // Stream finished normally\n    startPtzImagePoll();\n});\n```\n\nBut wait, the current outer code returns pump() inside a .then():\n```javascript\nfetch(endpoint, ...)\n    .then(function(resp) {\n        var reader = resp.body.getReader();\n        // ...\n        return pump();  // This returns a promise\n    })\n    .catch(function(e) {\n        // handle error\n    });\n```\n\nSo I can add `.finally()`:\n```javascript\nfetch(endpoint, ...)\n    .then(function(resp) {\n        var reader = resp.body.getReader();\n        // ...\n        return pump();  // Returns promise that resolves when stream done\n    })\n    .catch(function(e) {\n        // handle error\n    })\n    .finally(function() {\n        // Always run after stream is done or error\n        startPtzImagePoll();\n    });\n```\n\nBut the current code has `startPtzImagePoll()` in 4 different event branches inside the event handlers. These events might do UI updates that should happen BEFORE `startPtzImagePoll()`. \n\nActually, looking at the code, the `startPtzImagePoll()` calls are at the end of each event handler. So the UI updates happen first, then the polling resumes. Using `.finally()` should work because the event handlers complete before the `.finally()` runs.\n\nLet me now implement this. I need to:\n1. Remove all 4 `startPtzImagePoll()` calls from inside event handlers\n2. Add `.finally()` after the `.catch()`\n3. Keep `stopPtzImagePoll()` at the start (replace with `pausePtzPolling()`)\n\nWait, actually, looking at the boss's instructions: \"局部搜索的4个恢复分支集中到一个 finally，保持复用\"\n\nSo the boss wants:\n- Use a `.finally()` block (or equivalent) to consolidate the 4 recovery points\n- Keep the existing logic but just centralize the polling resume\n\nAnd also: \"同时，执行function/limit/speed期间暂停 ptzPositionPoll\"\n\nSo I need to use the new `pausePtzPolling()`/`resumePtzPolling()` functions which pause BOTH polls.\n\nLet me now make the actual edits.\n\nFor the _finishRegion function in index.html, I need to:\n1. Replace `stopPtzImagePoll()` with `pausePtzPolling()`\n2. Remove all 4 `startPtzImagePoll()` calls from event handlers\n3. Add `.finally(() => { resumePtzPolling(); })` after the `.catch()`\n4. Remove the `startPtzImagePoll()` from `.catch()` as well\n\nLet me look at the actual code again. I need to be very precise with the edit.\n\nActually wait, I also need to update `stopAdvTest()` and `pollAdvProgress()` in advanced.html. Let me plan all edits:\n\n1. **console.html**: Add pausePtzPolling/resumePtzPolling ✅ (done)\n2. **index.html**: \n   - Replace `stopPtzImagePoll()` with `pausePtzPolling()` in _finishRegion\n   - Remove all `startPtzImagePoll()` from event handlers (done, cleanup, error, interrupt)\n   - Add `.finally()` after `.catch()` with `resumePtzPolling()`\n   - Remove `startPtzImagePoll()` from `.catch()`\n3. **advanced.html**:\n   - Add `pausePtzPolling()` in `runAdvTest()` (before fetch)\n   - Add `resumePtzPolling()` in `pollAdvProgress()` (completed, failed, cancelled)\n   - Add `resumePtzPolling()` in `stopAdvTest()`\n4. **constants.py**: Update version to 8.66\n\nLet me proceed step by step. First, let me read the exact code in index.html around the _finishRegion function to make precise edits.\n\nActually, let me be smarter about this. Let me look at the structure of the _finishRegion function to understand what exactly I need to change.\n\nLooking at the code from earlier reads, the structure is:\n\n```javascript\nfunction _finishRegion() {\n    // ...\n    // v8.65: 流程开始，暂停主控台轮询\n    stopPtzImagePoll();\n\n    // ... SSE processing ...\n    \n    fetch(endpoint, { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: body })\n        .then(function(resp) {\n            // ...\n            function pump() {\n                return reader.read().then(function(r) {\n                    if (r.done) return;\n                    // ... process events ...\n                    return pump();\n                });\n            }\n            return pump();\n        })\n        .catch(function(e) {\n            // ...\n            startPtzImagePoll();  // <-- remove this\n        });\n}\n```\n\nWait, I need to check: is there a `startPtzImagePoll()` in `.catch()`? Let me look at the code I read earlier...\n\nFrom the earlier read (line 3005+):\n```javascript\n.catch(function(e) {\n    operationLog(label + '异常: ' + e.message, 'error');\n    showToast('error', '异常: ' + e.message);\n    // v8.41: 恢复停止按钮为灰色\n    if (stopBtn) { stopBtn.disabled = true; stopBtn.style.opacity = '0.5'; }\n    var toggleId = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'wbTimerToggle' : 'focusTimerToggle'; var toggleEl = document.getElementById(toggleId); if (toggleEl) { toggleEl.checked = false; }\n    // v8.65: 流程异常结束，恢复主控台轮询\n    startPtzImagePoll();\n});\n```\n\nYes, there's `startPtzImagePoll()` in `.catch()`.\n\nNow, the tricky part: I need to replace `.catch(...)` with `.catch(...).finally(...)` but the `.catch()` block currently has `startPtzImagePoll()` inside it. I need to:\n1. Remove `startPtzImagePoll()` from inside `.catch()`\n2. Add `.finally(function() { resumePtzPolling(); })` at the end\n\nActually, I can just chain `.finally()` after the `.catch()` and remove the `startPtzImagePoll()` from inside `.catch()`.\n\nLet me think about the exact edit:\n\nCurrent:\n```javascript\n})\n.catch(function(e) {\n    // ... handle error\n    startPtzImagePoll();\n});\n```\n\nAfter:\n```javascript\n})\n.catch(function(e) {\n    // ... handle error (without startPtzImagePoll)\n})\n.finally(function() {\n    resumePtzPolling();\n});\n```\n\nNow for the event handlers inside pump(), I need to remove the `startPtzImagePoll()` calls. Let me identify all 4 locations:\n\n1. `if (ev.type === 'done') { ... startPtzImagePoll(); }`\n2. `if (ev.type === 'cleanup') { ... startPtzImagePoll(); }`\n3. `if (ev.type === 'error') { ... startPtzImagePoll(); }`\n4. `if (ev.type === 'interrupt') { ... startPtzImagePoll(); }`\n\nActually, looking at the code again, these might be `else if` chains. Let me check.\n\nFrom the earlier read:\n```javascript\nif (ev.type === 'done') {\n    // ...\n    if (ev.final_red !== undefined) {\n        // wb done\n    } else {\n        // focus done\n    }\n    // ... UI updates ...\n    // v8.65: 流程结束，恢复主控台轮询\n    startPtzImagePoll();\n} else if (ev.type === 'cleanup') {\n    operationLog('清理完成', 'info');\n    // v8.65: 流程结束，恢复主控台轮询\n    startPtzImagePoll();\n} else if (ev.type === 'error') {\n    // ...\n    // v8.65: 流程结束，恢复主控台轮询\n    startPtzImagePoll();\n} else if (ev.type === 'interrupt') {\n    // ...\n    // v8.65: 流程结束，恢复主控台轮询\n    startPtzImagePoll();\n}\n```\n\nSo each of these branches has `startPtzImagePoll()` at the end. I need to remove all of them.\n\nBut wait, the `startPtzImagePoll()` inside `done` branch might be needed for the UI refresh that happens before `cleanup`. Let me check:\n\nLooking at the sequence: done → cleanup. So:\n1. `done` event: UI updated, `startPtzImagePoll()` called\n2. `cleanup` event: `startPtzImagePoll()` called again (idempotent)\n\nIf I remove both and move to `.finally()`, the UI updates still happen in the event handlers, and the polling resumes at the very end. Since `startPtzImagePoll()` is idempotent, calling it once at the end is fine.\n\nBut wait, there's a subtle issue: what if an `error` event happens without a subsequent `cleanup`? Let me check the backend:\n\nIn autofocus.py, the `run()` method ends with:\n```python\n# 4. 清理\nawait asyncio.to_thread(self._cleanup_func, \"Focus\", self.device_ip)\nyield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'cleanup'})}\\n\\n\"\n```\n\nAnd if an error occurs during the loop:\n```python\nif (r.done) return; // reader done\n// ... process events ...\n// if there's an error, it would be yielded as a 'type': 'error' event\n```\n\nActually, the backend might yield an `error` event but still yield `cleanup` afterwards. Or it might not. Let me check...\n\nLooking at the backend code for FocusSearcher.run():\n```python\nwhile True:\n    if self._interrupted:\n        // ... yield interrupt ...\n        break\n    // ... process ...\n    if cmd[\"action\"] == \"stop\":\n        // ... yield done ...\n        break\n\n// cleanup after loop\nawait asyncio.to_thread(self._cleanup_func, \"Focus\", self.device_ip)\nyield f\"data: {json.dumps({'type': 'cleanup'})}\\n\\n\"\n```\n\nSo `cleanup` is always yielded after the loop ends, regardless of how it ended (done or interrupt). And `error` is yielded inside the loop if there's an error.\n\nSo the sequence is always:\n- Normal: start → focus/wb × N → done → cleanup\n- Error: start → ... → error → (no cleanup? or yes cleanup?)\n\nWait, in the error case:\n- The backend might yield an error event and then the stream might close\n- Or it might yield error, then break, then cleanup\n\nLooking at the backend code more carefully:\n```python\nwhile True:\n    if self._interrupted:\n        yield \"data: ...\\n\\n\"  # interrupt event\n        break\n    // ...\n    if bgr is None:\n        yield \"data: ...error...\\n\\n\"  # error event\n        break\n    // ...\n    if cmd[\"action\"] == \"stop\":\n        yield \"data: ...done...\\n\\n\"\n        break\n\n# After loop\nawait asyncio.to_thread(self._cleanup_func, ...)\nyield \"data: ...cleanup...\\n\\n\"\n```\n\nSo `cleanup` is always yielded after the loop, even after error. The sequence would be: error → cleanup.\n\nAnd in the interrupt case: interrupt → ... → (break from loop) → cleanup.\n\nSo `.finally()` with `resumePtzPolling()` should be safe - it will always run after the stream ends, regardless of the event sequence.\n\nNow let me implement. First, let me read the exact code from index.html to make precise edits.\n\nActually, I think I need to read the code in index.html more carefully. Let me get the exact lines.\n\nLet me read lines around 2926 to 3040 in index.html, which is the _finishRegion function.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"**步骤2：修改 index.html 中的局部搜索流程**\n\n先读取需要修改的具体代码："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:51","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":120,"offset":2915,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":76208,"output":3984,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80192,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783449355859,"responseId":"cht000d3529@dx19f3ddda2172872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"39079b06","parentId":"8e99c620","timestamp":"2026-07-07T18:37:17.029Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.read:51","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        localStorage.setItem(regionKey, JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh }));\r\n        \r\n        var endpoint = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-search'\r\n                                               : '/api/v1/vision/focus-search';\r\n        var label = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '白平衡' : '对焦';\r\n\r\n        _resetRegionUI();\r\n        showToast('info', label + '迭代中...');\r\n        operationLog('── ' + label + '迭代开始 ──', 'info');\r\n        \r\n        // v8.65: 流程开始，暂停主控台轮询\r\n        stopPtzImagePoll();\r\n\r\n        // v8.41: 搜索启动时启用停止按钮\r\n        var stopBtnId = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'btnWbLocalStop' : 'btnFocusLocalStop';\r\n        var stopBtn = document.getElementById(stopBtnId);\r\n        if (stopBtn) { stopBtn.disabled = false; stopBtn.style.opacity = '1'; }\r\n\r\n        // SSE 流式调用\r\n        var body = JSON.stringify({ x: sx, y: sy, w: sw, h: sh });\r\n        fetch(endpoint, { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: body })\r\n            .then(function(resp) {\r\n                if (!resp.ok) throw new Error('HTTP ' + resp.status);\r\n                var reader = resp.body.getReader();\r\n                var decoder = new TextDecoder();\r\n                var buf = '';\r\n                function pump() {\r\n                    return reader.read().then(function(r) {\r\n                        if (r.done) return;\r\n                        buf += decoder.decode(r.value, { stream: true });\r\n                        // 按 \\n\\n 分割事件\r\n                        var parts = buf.split('\\n\\n');\r\n                        buf = parts.pop();  // 最后一段可能不完整\r\n                        for (var i = 0; i < parts.length; i++) {\r\n                            var line = parts[i];\r\n                            if (!line.startsWith('data: ')) continue;\r\n                            try {\r\n                                var ev = JSON.parse(line.slice(6));\r\n                                if (ev.type === 'start') {\r\n                                    operationLog(label + '开始, ' + ev.crop, 'info');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'wb') {\r\n                                    operationLog('调整 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.stage\r\n                                        + ' R=' + ev.red_gain + ' B=' + ev.blue_gain\r\n                                        + ' → R=' + ev.r_avg + ' G=' + ev.g_avg + ' B=' + ev.b_avg\r\n                                        + ' (Δ=' + ev.delta + ')', 'debug');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'focus') {\r\n                                    operationLog('对焦 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.stage\r\n                                        + ' ' + ev.action + ' 反差=' + ev.contrast\r\n                                        + ' (' + ev.duration + 's) ' + ev.message, 'debug');\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'done') {\r\n                                    if (ev.final_red !== undefined) {\r\n                                        showToast('success', label + '完成 R=' + ev.final_red + ' B=' + ev.final_blue);\r\n                                        operationLog('── ' + label + '完成: R=' + ev.final_red + ' B=' + ev.final_blue + ' (' + ev.total_steps + '步) ──', 'success');\r\n                                        // 刷新主控台白平衡滑动条\r\n                                        var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\r\n                                        var wbBlue = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\r\n                                        var wbRedVal = document.getElementById('wbRedVal');\r\n                                        var wbBlueVal = document.getElementById('wbBlueVal');\r\n                                        if (wbRed) { wbRed.value = ev.final_red; if (wbRedVal) wbRedVal.textContent = ev.final_red; }\r\n                                        if (wbBlue) { wbBlue.value = ev.final_blue; if (wbBlueVal) wbBlueVal.textContent = ev.final_blue; }\r\n                                    } else {\r\n                                        var rollMsg = ev.rollback_steps ? ' (回滚' + ev.rollback_steps + '步)' : '';\r\n                                        showToast('success', label + '完成 反差=' + ev.final_contrast + rollMsg);\r\n                                        operationLog('── ' + label + '完成: 反差=' + ev.final_contrast + rollMsg + ' (' + ev.total_steps + '步) ──', 'success');\r\n                                    }\r\n                                    // v8.41: 搜索完成后恢复停止按钮为灰色\r\n                                    if (stopBtn) { stopBtn.disabled = true; stopBtn.style.opacity = '0.5'; }\r\n                                    var toggleId = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'wbTimerToggle' : 'focusTimerToggle'; var toggleEl = document.getElementById(toggleId); if (toggleEl) { toggleEl.checked = false; }\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'cleanup') {\r\n                                    operationLog('清理完成', 'info');\r\n                                    // v8.65: 流程结束，恢复主控台轮询\r\n                                    startPtzImagePoll();\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'error') {\r\n                                    operationLog(label + '失败: ' + ev.message, 'error');\r\n                                    showToast('error', label + '失败');\r\n                                    // v8.41: 搜索失败后恢复停止按钮为灰色\r\n                                    if (stopBtn) { stopBtn.disabled = true; stopBtn.style.opacity = '0.5'; }\r\n                                    var toggleId = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'wbTimerToggle' : 'focusTimerToggle'; var toggleEl = document.getElementById(toggleId); if (toggleEl) { toggleEl.checked = false; }\r\n                                    // v8.65: 流程结束，恢复主控台轮询\r\n                                    startPtzImagePoll();\r\n                                } else if (ev.type === 'interrupt') {\r\n                                    // v8.41: 用户停止\r\n                                    operationLog(label + ': ' + ev.message, 'warning');\r\n                                    showToast('warning', label + '已停止');\r\n                                    if (ev.final_red !== undefined) {\r\n                                        var wbRed2 = document.getElementById('wbRed');\r\n                                        var wbBlue2 = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\r\n                                        var wbRedVal2 = document.getElementById('wbRedVal');\r\n                                        var wbBlueVal2 = document.getElementById('wbBlueVal');\r\n                                        if (wbRed2) { wbRed2.value = ev.final_red; if (wbRedVal2) wbRedVal2.textContent = ev.final_red; }\r\n                                        if (wbBlue2) { wbBlue2.value = ev.final_blue; if (wbBlueVal2) wbBlueVal2.textContent = ev.final_blue; }\r\n                                    }\r\n                                    // 恢复停止按钮为灰色\r\n                                    if (stopBtn) { stopBtn.disabled = true; stopBtn.style.opacity = '0.5'; }\r\n                                    var toggleId = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'wbTimerToggle' : 'focusTimerToggle'; var toggleEl = document.getElementById(toggleId); if (toggleEl) { toggleEl.checked = false; }\r\n                                    // v8.65: 流程结束，恢复主控台轮询\r\n                                    startPtzImagePoll();\r\n                                }\r\n                            } catch(e) { /* 跳过损坏的 JSON */ }\r\n                        }\r\n                        return pump();\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n                return pump();\r\n            })\r\n            .catch(function(e) {\r\n                operationLog(label + '异常: ' + e.message, 'error');\r\n                showToast('error', '异常: ' + e.message);\r\n                // v8.41: 恢复停止按钮为灰色\r\n                if (stopBtn) { stopBtn.disabled = true; stopBtn.style.opacity = '0.5'; }\r\n                var toggleId = mode === 'whitebalance' ? 'wbTimerToggle' : 'focusTimerToggle'; var toggleEl = document.getElementById(toggleId); if (toggleEl) { toggleEl.checked = false; }\r\n                // v8.65: 流程异常结束，恢复主控台轮询\r\n                startPtzImagePoll();\r\n            });\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    function _resetRegionUI() {\r\n        _regionMode = null;\r\n        var btnWB = document.getElementById('btnWbRegionSelect');\r\n        var btnAF = document.getElementById('btnFocusRegionSelect');\r\n\n[54 more lines in file. Use offset=3035 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783449437029}}
