{"type":"message","id":"3c210b0b","parentId":"28c09455","timestamp":"2026-07-07T19:15:11.431Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The boss is asking me to clarify which file the polling (ptzImagePoll) is implemented in, and to understand the branching structure. Let me think about this carefully.\n\nThe ptzImagePoll function (which polls PTZ position, whitebalance R/B, noise reduction, iris, shutter) is defined in `console.html`. It's the main console's periodic polling.\n\nNow, the local focus/white balance search code exists in TWO places:\n\n1. **index.html** - `_finishRegion()` function: This is the MANUAL box-selection flow. User draws a box on the video, clicks confirm, and the search starts. I've already updated this one with pausePtzPolling/resumePtzPolling.\n\n2. **console.html** - `executeScheduledSearch()` function: This is the TIMER-triggered flow. User sets a timer (e.g., auto WB every 5 minutes), and when the timer fires, it starts the search. This still uses the old `stopPtzImagePoll()`/`startPtzImagePoll()` pattern.\n\nThe boss is asking me to confirm which file I should be modifying. The answer is clear: I need to modify BOTH files:\n- **index.html** - `_finishRegion()` ✅ already done\n- **console.html** - `executeScheduledSearch()` ❌ still needs updating\n\nLet me also check: is there any other place that calls stopPtzImagePoll/startPtzImagePoll that I might have missed?\n\nFrom my earlier search:\n- console.html:676 - disableImageControls() → KEEP (device disconnect)\n- console.html:747 - enableImageControls() → KEEP (device connect)\n- console.html:1478 - executeScheduledSearch() → NEED UPDATE\n- console.html:1547 - executeScheduledSearch() → NEED UPDATE\n- console.html:1552 - executeScheduledSearch() → NEED UPDATE\n- console.html:1990 - function definition → already added pausePtzPolling/resumePtzPolling\n- console.html:2061 - function definition → same\n\nAnd in index.html:\n- index.html:1498 - stopPtzPositionPoll in device disconnect → KEEP\n- index.html:2381/2389 - position poll definitions → KEEP\n- index.html:2926 - _finishRegion → ✅ already updated\n\nSo I need to update `executeScheduledSearch()` in console.html. Let me be clear and concise about this to the boss.\n\nAlso, the boss asked me to \"搞清楚分支结构\" (understand the branch structure). Let me explain:\n\nThere are TWO entry points for local focus/white balance search:\n1. Manual: User draws a box → `_finishRegion()` in index.html → SSE search\n2. Timer: Timer fires → `executeScheduledSearch()` in console.html → SSE search\n\nBoth need to pause/resume polling. I've done #1, still need to do #2.\n\nLet me respond concisely.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"两个入口，两个文件：\n\n```\n局部搜索触发路径:\n├── ① 手动框选 → index.html::_finishRegion()  ✅ 已改\n└── ② 定时触发 → console.html::executeScheduledSearch()  ❌ 未改\n```\n\n轮询定义在 `console.html`（`startPtzImagePoll`/`stopPtzImagePoll`），统一封装器也已加在 `console.html`。\n\n需要改 `console.html` 的 `executeScheduledSearch`：`stopPtzImagePoll` → `pausePtzPolling`，`startPtzImagePoll` → `resumePtzPolling`。马上改。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_iyyr65j5mxbzeu0eg9bo3rc1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    // v8.66: 流程开始，暂停主控台轮询\n    pausePtzPolling();","oldText":"    // v8.65: 流程开始，暂停主控台轮询\n    stopPtzImagePoll();"},{"newText":"            // v8.66: 流程结束，恢复主控台轮询\n            resumePtzPolling();","oldText":"            // v8.65: 流程结束，恢复主控台轮询\n            startPtzImagePoll();"},{"newText":"            // v8.66: 流程异常，恢复主控台轮询\n            resumePtzPolling();","oldText":"            // v8.65: 流程异常，恢复主控台轮询\n            startPtzImagePoll();"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":107085,"output":1046,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108131,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"to