{"type":"message","id":"ef6503ec","parentId":"b69942be","timestamp":"2026-07-07T19:27:46.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The boss asked me to verify. The verification is complete and shows:\n\n1. **VERSION**: v8.66 ✅\n2. **Backup**: 4 files backed up ✅\n3. **Old calls**: No remaining old-style calls in search-related code ✅ (only disable/enableImageControls which are correct to keep)\n\nThe old calls filter returned nothing, meaning all `startPtzImagePoll`/`stopPtzImagePoll` calls in search-related code have been replaced. The only remaining calls are in the function definitions and `disableImageControls()`/`enableImageControls()` which are for device connect/disconnect.\n\nNow let me write a clean completion report for the boss.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"验证结果：\n\n```\n✅ VERSION = v8.66 (constants.py)\n✅ 备份完成: 4个文件 (backup_20260708_poll-pause/)\n✅ 旧调用清零: 搜索相关代码中无残留的 startPtzImagePoll/stopPtzImagePoll\n```\n\n**修改汇总 (v8.66)**：\n\n| 文件 | 修改 | 行数 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `console.html` | 新增 `pausePtzPolling()`/`resumePtzPolling()` 封装器 + 全局导出 | +22 |\n| `console.html` | `executeScheduledSearch()` 替换为 `pausePtzPolling()`/`resumePtzPolling()` | 3处 |\n| `index.html` | `_finishRegion()` 替换为 `pausePtzPolling()`，4个恢复分支集中到 `.finally(resumePtzPolling)` | 1处 |\n| `advanced.html` | `runAdvTest()` 添加 `pausePtzPolling()`，3个完成状态 + `stopAdvTest()` 添加 `resumePtzPolling()` | 5处 |\n| `constants.py` | 版本号 `v8.65` → `v8.66` | 1处 |\n\n**死代码清理**：无（`stopPtzImagePoll`/`startPtzImagePoll` 保留在 `disable/enableImageControls()` 中，用于设备连接/断开控制）\n\n修复完成。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":117055,"output":444,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117499,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783452436923,"responseId":"cht000de368@dx19f3e0c91e62871503"}}
