{"type":"message","id":"52f1b2e0","parentId":"6cc725e0","timestamp":"2026-07-07T19:36:58.091Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The boss wants me to do a retrospective (复盘) and update memory. Let me follow the AGENTS.md rules:\n\n1. 抽象近期犯的错误模式（不是具体操作，而是方法论问题）\n2. 提炼学到的新方法/逻辑\n3. 写出具体修改了什么、改到哪个文件\n4. 不能只回复\"复盘完成\"，必须列出具体变更\n\nThen update memory:\n1. 将复盘中涉及的教训写入 `.learnings/ERRORS.md` 或 `.learnings/LEARNINGS.md`\n2. 跨任务通用的教训晋升到 `SOUL.md` / `AGENTS.md` / `MEMORY.md`\n3. 项目特定内容写入 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n\nLet me think about what went well and what could be improved:\n\n**What went well:**\n- Properly analyzed the code before making changes\n- Identified both entry points (manual box selection and timer-triggered search)\n- Used a counter-based pause/resume mechanism for robustness\n- Consolidated 4 recovery branches into a single `.finally()` block\n- Paused both ptzImagePoll AND ptzPositionPoll during operations\n- Cleaned up dead code\n\n**Errors/issues during this session:**\n1. Initially only modified index.html's _finishRegion, forgetting that executeScheduledSearch in console.html is a separate code path. Boss had to remind me to check which file the polling is in.\n2. Got confused with the branch structure at first - didn't immediately realize there were TWO separate search entry points\n3. The PowerShell commands kept failing due to encoding issues and syntax errors - should use simpler approaches\n\n**Key learnings:**\n1. When modifying a mechanism that exists in multiple places, always grep ALL files first to find every instance\n2. Before refactoring, map out all entry points and call paths\n3. PowerShell in this environment has encoding issues with Chinese characters - use Write-Host instead of echo, or use simpler commands\n\nLet me also think about what needs to go where:\n- `.learnings/LEARNINGS.md`: The lesson about mapping all entry points before modifying shared mechanisms\n- `.learnings/ERRORS.md`: The initial oversight of missing the executeScheduledSearch code path\n- `memory/2026-07-08.md`: Today's work record\n- HEARTBEAT.md: Update with v8.66 changes\n\nLet me also check if any lesson should be promoted to self-improving memory or corrections.\n\nActually, the main error was: I started modifying without fully mapping out all the code paths that call stopPtzImagePoll/startPtzImagePoll. I should have done a comprehensive grep first.\n\nLet me write the retrospective and then update the memory files.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_k9u09czwrsyxfu8u7z0s3xlz","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\.learnings\\LEARNINGS.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ncbryl3t9j7kf2hqw69mttb1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\.learnings\\ERRORS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":131719,"output":717,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132436,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783452993758,"responseId":"cht000dc7fc@dx19f3e1519832872503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"966ed4c7","parentId":"52f1b2e0","timestamp":"2026-07-07T19:36:58.100Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_k9u09czwrsyxfu8u7z0s3xlz","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# LEARNINGS.md - 教训与洞察\n\n## LRN-20260628-001: 双 PTZController 类是 opencode 分叉遗留\n\n**时间**: 2026-06-28\n**优先级**: CRITICAL\n**状态**: VERIFIED\n**领域**: 架构\n\n### 发现\n`src/core/ptz_controller.py` 内置了一个 PTZController 类（L900-L1206），\n是 opencode 克隆的独立副本。与 `src/ptz/isapi/ptz.py` 的正版是两套代码。\nPTZDeviceController 内部 `self._controllers[ip] = PTZController(client)` \n走的是副本而非正版——意味着正版新增的方法（setup_home_preset、goto_home_and_wait等）\n在 connect_device 路径中不可用。\n\n### 修复\n1. 删除 core 中的 PTZController 副本，改为 `from src.ptz.isapi.ptz import PTZController`\n2. 迁移副本独有的2个方法（focus_move_continuous、focus_stop）到正版\n3. 删除 ptz/__init__.py 和 ptz/core/__init__.py 的循环导入\n\n[738 more lines in file. Use offset=21 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783453018100}}
{"type":"message","id":"4432fd07","parentId":"966ed4c7","timestamp":"2026-07-07T19:36:58.100Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ncbryl3t9j7kf2hqw69mttb1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 复盘：v7.109 → v7.111 录制功能灾难\n\n**日期**: 2026-06-24\n**任务**: 录制功能修复\n**结果**: 4次迭代才稳定，犯多个严重错误\n\n---\n\n## 我犯了什么错\n\n### 1. 擅自删除工作的WASM录制方案（最严重）\n\n老板没让我改录制方案。v7.106 的 WASM 录制已经在工作。\n\n我做了什么：\n- **擅自判断** ISAPI 后端录制比 WASM 好\n- **擅自删除** `wasmCapturePic` / `wasmStartRecord` / `wasmStopRecord` 函数\n- 改用 ISAPI `/ContentMgmt/record/control/manual/start` 控制命令\n- 后果：录制功能完全失效，因为摄像头没有SD卡\n\n**教训**：只改老板要求的逻辑。没坏的不要修。\n\n### 2. 不理解ISAPI机制就做决定\n\n| API | 机制 | 数据流向 |\n|-----|------|----------|\n| `GET /ISAPI/Streaming/Channels/{channel}/picture` | 截图 | 摄像头 → HTTP响应 → 服务器 ✅ |\n| `PUT /ISAPI/ContentMgmt/record/control/manual/start` | 录像命令 | 摄像头内部录制 ❌（数据不返回） |\n\n**根因**：截图和录像的ISAPI API机制完全不同。截图返回数据，录像是控制命令。我假设两者类似，直接套用，完全错误。\n\n[122 more lines in file. Use offset=31 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783453018100}}
{"type":"message","id":"057c3e5e","parentId":"4432fd07","timestamp":"2026-07-07T19:37:32.385Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me write the retrospective and update the memory files. Let me be concise and follow the format:\n\n1. First, write the retrospective in my response to the boss\n2. Then update .learnings/ERRORS.md with the new error\n3. Update memory/2026-07-08.md with today's work\n4. Update HEARTBEAT.md with v8.66\n\nLet me think about the key lessons:\n\n**Error pattern**: 修改共享机制时，没有先全局搜索所有调用点。只改了 index.html 的 _finishRegion，漏掉了 console.html 的 executeScheduledSearch。老板提醒后才补上。\n\n**Root cause**: 假设搜索代码只在 index.html 中，没有验证。应该先 `grep stopPtzImagePoll` 全项目找所有调用点，画出完整调用图再修改。\n\n**Lesson**: 修改跨文件的共享机制前，必须先 grep 全项目确认所有使用点，画出调用拓扑图。\n\n**What went right**: \n- 计数器保护的 pause/resume 封装器设计正确\n- .finally() 统一恢复点简洁\n- 同时暂停了 ptzImagePoll 和 ptzPositionPoll\n- 备份 + 版本号迭代规范执行\n\nLet me write this up.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"## 复盘 v8.66\n\n### 本次错误\n\n**① 修改前未全量搜索调用点**\n\n- 只改了 `index.html::_finishRegion`，漏掉 `console.html::executeScheduledSearch`\n- 老板提醒\"搞清楚分支结构\"后才意识到搜索有**两个入口**（手动框选 + 定时触发）\n- **根因**：假设代码只有一条路径，没验证\n\n**正确做法**：改共享机制前 → `grep 目标函数名 所有文件` → 画出调用拓扑 → 逐点修改\n\n### 本次正确\n\n| 做法 | 效果 |\n|------|------|\n| 计数器保护 pause/resume | 嵌套调用不互相干扰 |\n| `.finally()` 统一恢复 | 4个恢复点 → 1个 |\n| 同时暂停两种轮询 | ptzImagePoll + ptzPositionPoll |\n| 备份+版本号 | 规范执行 |\n\n### 具体修改\n\n| 文件 | 行 | 内容 |\n|------|-----|------|\n| `console.html` | 2069-2090 | 新增 `pausePtzPolling`/`resumePtzPolling` |\n| `console.html` | 1478/1547/1552 | `executeScheduledSearch` 替换旧调用 |\n| `index.html` | 2926 | `_finishRegion` 替换为 `pausePtzPolling` |\n| `index.html` | 3023 | 4个恢复分支 → `.finally(resumePtzPolling)` |\n| `advanced.html` | 307 | `runAdvTest` 添加 `pausePtzPolling` |\n| `advanced.html` | 344/812/828/843 | 4个退出路径添加 `resumePtzPolling` |\n| `constants.py` | 13 | `v8.64` → `v8.66` |\n\n---\n\n现在写入记忆文件。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3chwpthepj9w4avr5ckrcoda","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"# ERRORS.md - 错误记录\n\n## ERR-20260708-001: 修改共享机制前未全量搜索调用点\n\n**时间**: 2026-07-08\n**任务**: 主控台轮询暂停机制\n**错误**: 只改了 index.html 的 _finishRegion，漏掉 console.html 的 executeScheduledSearch\n**老板纠正**: \"搞清楚分支结构\" → 搜索有2个入口（手动框选+定时触发）\n**根因**: 假设只有一条代码路径，没有 grep 全项目确认所有 stopPtzImagePoll 调用点\n**修复**: 补上 console.html 的 executeScheduledSearch 替换\n**教训**: 改跨文件的共享机制前，必须先 grep 全项目画出调用拓扑图，逐点修改\n\n---\n\n# 复盘：v7.109 → v7.111 录制功能灾难","oldText":"# 复盘：v7.109 → v7.111 录制功能灾难"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\.learnings\\ERRORS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"qwen-3.7-max","usage":{"input":133073,"output":992,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134065,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783453018102,"responseId":"cht000de39c@dx19f3e158bdd29bb503"}}
